WEBVTT

1
00:00:46.292 --> 00:00:48.904
Humans are essentially a
bunch of electrical signals.

2
00:00:49.571 --> 00:00:51.375
Your perception of this world.

3
00:00:51.376 --> 00:00:53.000
your memory.

4
00:00:53.001 --> 00:00:55.334
is all getting into here.

5
00:00:55.335 --> 00:00:57.043
right through this wire.

6
00:00:58.460 --> 00:00:59.928
Yes. right here.

7
00:01:05.959 --> 00:01:07.542
Fuck it.

8
00:01:07.543 --> 00:01:08.834
I'm not escaping.

9
00:01:08.835 --> 00:01:12.292
I don't care any fucking
problems 100 years from now.

10
00:01:12.293 --> 00:01:13.418
This is not my problem!

11
00:01:14.877 --> 00:01:18.877
This is the technology
keeping human civilization alive.

12
00:01:20.002 --> 00:01:21.959
I'm building a new world!

13
00:01:21.960 --> 00:01:23.061
Why is it forbidden?

14
00:01:24.377 --> 00:01:25.377
Why?

15
00:01:31.335 --> 00:01:33.334
Your body is fragile.

16
00:01:33.335 --> 00:01:34.502
It gets hurt.

17
00:01:34.503 --> 00:01:35.710
It gets sick.

18
00:01:35.711 --> 00:01:36.711
It gets old.

19
00:01:37.711 --> 00:01:38.960
It dies.

20
00:01:38.961 --> 00:01:41.127
It gets fucking depressed.

21
00:01:41.128 --> 00:01:42.335
But...

22
00:01:42.336 --> 00:01:47.253
the digital you can live
forever. theoretically.

23
00:01:51.128 --> 00:01:52.128
Initially.

24
00:01:53.086 --> 00:01:54.878
no one minded this disaster.

25
00:01:56.336 --> 00:01:57.961
It's just a wildfire.

26
00:01:59.878 --> 00:02:01.044
drought.

27
00:02:02.211 --> 00:02:03.711
species extinction.

28
00:02:05.086 --> 00:02:06.753
and disappearance of a city...

29
00:02:08.586 --> 00:02:15.629
until this disaster became
closely related to everyone.

30
00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:21.129
Listen.

31
00:02:21.837 --> 00:02:24.704
you didn't need guns in this place before.
[Libreville]

32
00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:27.629
You missed the good old days.

33
00:02:29.110 --> 00:02:30.254
This street...

34
00:02:31.086 --> 00:02:32.253
wasn't this way.

35
00:02:32.254 --> 00:02:33.336
It was...

36
00:02:33.337 --> 00:02:36.044
The night market was great.
[Liu Peiqiang]

37
00:02:36.045 --> 00:02:38.711
It was known as the Little
Northeast of Africa.

38
00:02:38.712 --> 00:02:40.360
Barbecue stalls were everywhere.

39
00:02:42.504 --> 00:02:44.420
It's fine. They're patrolling.

40
00:02:45.420 --> 00:02:47.711
The kunga cakes were this thick.

41
00:02:47.712 --> 00:02:51.004
There were 500.000 midges in a cake.
It was yummy.

42
00:02:51.005 --> 00:02:53.235
Now. you can't even eat midges anymore.

43
00:02:56.296 --> 00:02:57.962
We're here.

44
00:02:57.963 --> 00:02:59.361
This is where they are.

45
00:03:02.005 --> 00:03:03.545
Mr. Liu.

46
00:03:03.546 --> 00:03:04.546
Mrs. Liu.

47
00:03:06.130 --> 00:03:07.880
I brought Peiqiang to see you.
[Zhang Peng]

48
00:03:09.588 --> 00:03:10.838
This kid is promising.

49
00:03:12.095 --> 00:03:14.637
He passed our country's
Reserve Astronauts examination.

50
00:03:15.963 --> 00:03:18.046
Next. he's preparing to go to the Moon.

51
00:03:20.056 --> 00:03:21.630
He's training here now.

52
00:03:22.963 --> 00:03:24.296
Don't worry.

53
00:03:26.463 --> 00:03:27.963
I'll take good care of him.

54
00:03:41.964 --> 00:03:42.964
Chief.

55
00:03:43.756 --> 00:03:45.214
Is there really a Solar Crisis?

56
00:03:45.964 --> 00:03:46.964
You'll be blind.

57
00:03:49.297 --> 00:03:52.577
I guess so. They're already fighting this
way. [34 years to the solar helium flash]

58
00:03:54.464 --> 00:03:57.338
Anyway. Earth will be
swallowed up in 100 years

59
00:03:57.339 --> 00:03:59.213
and the solar system will
be destroyed in 300 years.

60
00:03:59.214 --> 00:04:00.588
That's it.

61
00:04:00.589 --> 00:04:01.766
What else can we do?

62
00:04:05.797 --> 00:04:06.797
Slow down.

63
00:04:12.006 --> 00:04:14.089
Are you ready to go to the Moon?

64
00:04:14.964 --> 00:04:18.173
Once you're there. you'll be
staying for 10 or 20 years.

65
00:04:18.965 --> 00:04:19.965
That's great.

66
00:04:21.715 --> 00:04:25.340
Our whole family will be in the sky.

67
00:04:28.382 --> 00:04:30.757
Anyway. Earth isn't nice at all.

68
00:04:32.090 --> 00:04:34.048
It's pretty nice just to be alive.

69
00:04:35.423 --> 00:04:36.757
Silly kid.

70
00:04:39.089 --> 00:04:40.506
Listen.

71
00:04:40.507 --> 00:04:41.507
Hang in there.

72
00:04:42.465 --> 00:04:44.089
Steadier!

73
00:04:44.090 --> 00:04:45.090
Steady!

74
00:04:59.174 --> 00:05:03.811
[The Moving Mountain Project]
[No.1 Planetary Test Engine]

75
00:05:06.387 --> 00:05:08.340
Did you see that?

76
00:05:08.341 --> 00:05:11.840
That's the Test Engine 1
of the Moving Mountain Project.

77
00:05:11.841 --> 00:05:14.008
We'll be done in less than six months.

78
00:05:15.048 --> 00:05:16.215
Six months?

79
00:05:16.216 --> 00:05:18.132
Can it be done in time?

80
00:05:18.133 --> 00:05:21.633
Listen. We can even build
engines on the Moon.

81
00:05:22.602 --> 00:05:24.132
We don't even need people.

82
00:05:24.133 --> 00:05:26.466
They're all automatically
done. non-stop. quick.

83
00:05:28.341 --> 00:05:32.133
As long as no one sabotages
it. six months is enough.

84
00:05:34.758 --> 00:05:35.674
Attention.

85
00:05:35.675 --> 00:05:39.895
ATC10171 is entering AA
inner circle Mark D2.

86
00:05:39.896 --> 00:05:40.953
Please confirm.

87
00:05:40.954 --> 00:05:43.718
IFF check pass. Stand down.

88
00:05:45.217 --> 00:05:47.884
The sun is rapidly aging.

89
00:05:48.717 --> 00:05:50.966
It continues to expand.

90
00:05:50.967 --> 00:05:55.009
A hundred years later. the sun will
expand to engulf the entire Earth.

91
00:05:56.342 --> 00:06:00.384
After 300 years. the solar
system will cease to exist.

92
00:06:02.675 --> 00:06:05.217
In response to the Solar
Crisis 100 years from now.

93
00:06:05.218 --> 00:06:07.635
A United Earth Government
was established...

94
00:06:09.925 --> 00:06:12.259
and dozens of crisis
response plans were proposed.

95
00:06:13.384 --> 00:06:15.674
To ensure that more people survive.

96
00:06:15.675 --> 00:06:21.217
the Moving Mountain Project finally
decided to build 10.000 Earth Engines

97
00:06:21.218 --> 00:06:23.885
to drive the Earth out of the solar system.

98
00:06:24.843 --> 00:06:29.759
At the same time. three satellite engines
were built to exile the Moon

99
00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:33.676
and guarantee the smooth departure of Earth
from the Moon's gravity.

100
00:06:34.926 --> 00:06:37.800
To verify the feasibility
of the Moving Mountain Project.

101
00:06:37.801 --> 00:06:42.467
33 countries co-founded the joint experiment bases
in Libreville and on the Moon's Campanus Crater.

102
00:06:42.468 --> 00:06:46.009
However. as the project progressed.

103
00:06:46.010 --> 00:06:48.675
the difficulty and high
cost of implementation

104
00:06:48.676 --> 00:06:52.300
intensified the impact of the interest
of all parties in the world.

105
00:06:52.301 --> 00:06:57.135
Doubts. oppositions. and conflicts
are escalating day by day.

106
00:06:57.136 --> 00:07:00.051
Another armed riot broke out
in the suburb of Libreville.

107
00:07:00.052 --> 00:07:03.343
UEG has sent peacekeeping
forces to quell it.

108
00:07:03.344 --> 00:07:05.718
Their equipment is getting
more and more advanced.

109
00:07:05.719 --> 00:07:07.968
There must be a state-level
armed forces behind them.

110
00:07:07.969 --> 00:07:13.010
The crisis response plan
became the crisis itself.

111
00:07:13.011 --> 00:07:15.518
The feasibility verification
of the Mountain Moving Project...

112
00:07:16.594 --> 00:07:18.089
is of utmost urgency.

113
00:07:23.427 --> 00:07:25.551
This is First Avenue. We've been attacked.

114
00:07:25.552 --> 00:07:27.463
I repeat. We have been attacked.

115
00:07:27.464 --> 00:07:28.551
[New York]

116
00:07:28.552 --> 00:07:31.926
This is UEG Avenue. We have
three officers injured.

117
00:07:31.927 --> 00:07:35.218
Calling for backup.
[UEG Headquarter Building]

118
00:07:35.219 --> 00:07:37.844
Location. UEG Building.

119
00:07:37.845 --> 00:07:41.108
There has been an explosion.
Requesting for backup.

120
00:07:41.109 --> 00:07:43.449
Send backup immediately.

121
00:07:47.428 --> 00:07:49.177
UEG has been attacked.

122
00:07:49.178 --> 00:07:51.095
Be careful in Philadelphia.

123
00:07:58.427 --> 00:07:59.969
Okay. got it.

124
00:07:59.970 --> 00:08:01.228
Please wait a moment.

125
00:08:04.136 --> 00:08:06.219
I think the Digital Life supporters did it.

126
00:08:06.220 --> 00:08:07.579
Excuse me.

127
00:08:09.178 --> 00:08:12.012
We shouldn't have banned
the Digital Life Project.

128
00:08:14.095 --> 00:08:16.137
Do we know the number of attackers?

129
00:08:18.971 --> 00:08:21.303
I don't give a damn! Just send someone.

130
00:08:21.304 --> 00:08:22.304
Sorry.

131
00:08:25.804 --> 00:08:29.596
Currently. 127 people from 53 countries were
arrested. [10 months to the first ignition]

132
00:08:31.112 --> 00:08:34.838
[Hao Xiaoxi]

133
00:08:35.929 --> 00:08:40.536
As of now. there are 17 reports of damage
on the UEG HQ building.

134
00:08:40.537 --> 00:08:42.970
the United Nations Avenue has 13.

135
00:08:42.971 --> 00:08:44.720
First Avenue has 21.

136
00:08:44.721 --> 00:08:46.803
5 on East 43rd Street.

137
00:08:46.804 --> 00:08:48.161
74 on East 44th Street...

138
00:08:48.162 --> 00:08:49.893
I'll cut to the chase.

139
00:08:51.540 --> 00:08:56.888
This attack on the UEG is an indication that
people have lost interest in the project.

140
00:08:58.014 --> 00:09:02.972
We advise postponement of
the Moving Mountain Project.

141
00:09:06.054 --> 00:09:07.388
Mike.

142
00:09:07.389 --> 00:09:08.870
That is a bad idea.

143
00:09:10.264 --> 00:09:13.473
The darkest hour is always before dawn.

144
00:09:17.505 --> 00:09:18.671
We suggest...

145
00:09:20.179 --> 00:09:24.930
continuing the construction and withstanding
all distractions and disruptions...

146
00:09:25.805 --> 00:09:27.805
to complete verification
as soon as possible.

147
00:09:29.221 --> 00:09:30.513
Don't forget.

148
00:09:30.514 --> 00:09:34.054
We only have a 13-month window.

149
00:09:34.055 --> 00:09:37.554
The sun won't wait for us.

150
00:09:37.555 --> 00:09:40.543
[Zhou Zhezhi]

151
00:09:47.765 --> 00:09:48.765
Qiangzi.

152
00:09:50.015 --> 00:09:54.055
Listen. The environment is very dangerous.
Do your best.

153
00:09:54.056 --> 00:09:57.676
Don't date. don't marry. don't have kids.
[UEG Joint Research Base. Gabon]

154
00:10:00.618 --> 00:10:03.347
- 1.428 young pilots...
- Don't worry. Chief.

155
00:10:03.348 --> 00:10:06.056
- From 33 different countries...
- I must roam space on behalf of mankind.

156
00:10:06.057 --> 00:10:08.913
Has successfully entered Gabon base

157
00:10:08.914 --> 00:10:12.972
to build up the talent pool
for the Moving Mountain Project.

158
00:10:12.973 --> 00:10:16.765
A large crowd of protesters
are gathered outside the base.

159
00:10:16.766 --> 00:10:21.057
protesting against the continuation
of the Moving Mountain Project.

160
00:10:25.931 --> 00:10:27.719
Get out of my way!

161
00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:28.604
Fire.

162
00:10:28.605 --> 00:10:30.516
I'm burning this place down!

163
00:10:39.985 --> 00:10:42.354
[Han Duoduo]

164
00:10:42.355 --> 00:10:44.521
"Han Duoduo".

165
00:11:00.350 --> 00:11:01.767
Is Earth nice or what?

166
00:11:07.016 --> 00:11:10.766
All armed personnel.
you've been surrounded.

167
00:11:10.767 --> 00:11:13.558
Drop your weapons at once and surrender.

168
00:11:19.259 --> 00:11:20.868
[Pass]

169
00:11:20.869 --> 00:11:23.102
Fuck off! I'm gonna burn this place now.

170
00:11:23.103 --> 00:11:24.814
Get the fuck out of my way!

171
00:11:29.308 --> 00:11:30.767
This thing can move.

172
00:11:30.768 --> 00:11:32.079
It moves when you move.

173
00:11:41.893 --> 00:11:43.225
Have you had breakfast?

174
00:11:43.226 --> 00:11:44.683
Yes.

175
00:11:44.684 --> 00:11:46.142
You'll vomit if you ate a lot.

176
00:11:46.143 --> 00:11:47.475
What?

177
00:11:47.476 --> 00:11:49.975
You'll get eliminated if you vomit later.

178
00:11:49.976 --> 00:11:51.018
What?

179
00:11:51.019 --> 00:11:54.505
[The Space Elevator]

180
00:11:54.506 --> 00:11:57.225
This is your first training in the air.

181
00:11:57.226 --> 00:12:00.433
Don't let your vomit block your windpipes.

182
00:12:00.434 --> 00:12:02.517
Get lost if you vomit.

183
00:12:02.518 --> 00:12:05.393
I won't perform CPR on you.

184
00:12:09.559 --> 00:12:11.724
Hello. I'm Han Duoduo.

185
00:12:11.725 --> 00:12:13.393
Low Earth Orbit Healthcare major.

186
00:12:14.351 --> 00:12:15.351
Hello.

187
00:12:16.268 --> 00:12:18.350
- Liu Peiqiang.
- Hey. beautiful.

188
00:12:18.351 --> 00:12:19.684
How are you doing?

189
00:12:19.685 --> 00:12:21.713
I am fine. Thank you.

190
00:12:21.714 --> 00:12:22.714
And you?

191
00:12:22.715 --> 00:12:24.393
As the Space Elevator ascends.

192
00:12:24.394 --> 00:12:26.537
- I'm annoyed.
- You'll sustain up to 9G.

193
00:12:26.538 --> 00:12:30.561
Earth won't go easy on you
just because you're trainees.

194
00:12:30.562 --> 00:12:32.434
Check your anti-G suits.

195
00:12:32.435 --> 00:12:34.472
Or your parents will end up in tears.

196
00:12:35.768 --> 00:12:38.101
Prepare to launch Space Elevator.

197
00:12:38.102 --> 00:12:40.059
All staff for final check.

198
00:12:40.060 --> 00:12:42.592
Ready to inflate anti-G suits.

199
00:12:42.593 --> 00:12:43.643
You know. beautiful.

200
00:12:43.644 --> 00:12:46.643
if you're afraid. you
can always hold my hand.

201
00:12:46.644 --> 00:12:48.519
Checking respiratory system.

202
00:12:49.644 --> 00:12:50.644
You too.

203
00:12:51.851 --> 00:12:53.059
You three.

204
00:12:53.060 --> 00:12:54.604
Launch countdown.

205
00:12:55.769 --> 00:12:57.769
Pedestrian bridge withdrawn.

206
00:12:58.644 --> 00:13:00.395
Cargo gate closing.

207
00:13:02.947 --> 00:13:04.769
Five.

208
00:13:04.770 --> 00:13:07.770
- Electromagnetic launch connected.
- Four.

209
00:13:07.771 --> 00:13:08.813
Three.

210
00:13:10.270 --> 00:13:11.270
Two.

211
00:13:12.645 --> 00:13:13.645
One.

212
00:13:14.936 --> 00:13:15.936
Launch.

213
00:13:35.103 --> 00:13:36.020
Breathe.

214
00:13:36.021 --> 00:13:37.102
Breathe.

215
00:13:37.103 --> 00:13:38.728
Pay attention to the frequency.

216
00:13:40.562 --> 00:13:42.145
Scream your lungs out. kids.

217
00:13:42.146 --> 00:13:45.978
You'll pass out within ten seconds.

218
00:13:45.979 --> 00:13:53.979
The 90.000 km Space Elevator is the
tallest architecture in human history.

219
00:13:55.354 --> 00:13:58.978
This is your starting point to the Moon.

220
00:13:58.979 --> 00:14:01.812
We're counting on you to
protect mankind's future.

221
00:14:17.978 --> 00:14:19.436
Pass granted.

222
00:14:19.437 --> 00:14:23.021
Passage through Cargo
Transfer Area granted.

223
00:14:23.022 --> 00:14:27.604
Welcome to Docking Area A7
of the Ark Space Station.

224
00:14:27.605 --> 00:14:29.313
We wish you a good day.

225
00:14:40.063 --> 00:14:43.187
[The Ark ISS - Under Construction]

226
00:14:43.188 --> 00:14:46.479
Three unauthorized individuals detected.

227
00:14:46.480 --> 00:14:49.396
Please strictly operate
in authorized area only.

228
00:14:49.397 --> 00:14:51.729
These three won't wake up anytime soon.

229
00:14:51.730 --> 00:14:55.356
During this one-month training.
they won't get much chance to sleep here.

230
00:14:56.160 --> 00:15:00.339
[29 days to the attack]

231
00:15:07.105 --> 00:15:09.000
Next.

232
00:15:09.001 --> 00:15:10.200
Hey. open.

233
00:15:12.397 --> 00:15:14.188
Breathe through the chest.

234
00:15:14.189 --> 00:15:16.122
Semi-closed slow breathing. twice as slow.

235
00:15:35.730 --> 00:15:37.063
Activate the electromagnetic gun.

236
00:15:37.064 --> 00:15:38.230
Lock on the target.

237
00:15:38.231 --> 00:15:41.399
If your hit rate is less
than 70%. get lost at once.

238
00:15:43.024 --> 00:15:44.064
Next.

239
00:15:44.065 --> 00:15:45.231
Give up.

240
00:15:45.232 --> 00:15:47.024
I want to get rid of half of you.

241
00:15:54.232 --> 00:15:55.607
Prepare your weapons.

242
00:16:05.024 --> 00:16:07.689
Congratulations. you two.
You passed the first exam.

243
00:16:07.690 --> 00:16:10.149
You're now chosen to be Lunar
Base astronaut trainees.

244
00:16:11.607 --> 00:16:14.481
Actually. it's not important to roam space.

245
00:16:14.482 --> 00:16:16.939
Giving flowers to the one
you like is important.

246
00:16:16.940 --> 00:16:18.201
You're so corny.

247
00:16:27.775 --> 00:16:29.441
Another 15 degrees...

248
00:16:30.525 --> 00:16:31.764
and it's perfect.

249
00:16:38.191 --> 00:16:41.399
2.27 degrees Celsius.

250
00:16:41.400 --> 00:16:43.869
Wind speed. 14 knots.

251
00:16:43.870 --> 00:16:46.357
- Wind heading. 210.
- They're watching closely. Can't do this.

252
00:16:46.358 --> 00:16:47.982
- Visibility.
- We'll be watching next time.

253
00:16:47.983 --> 00:16:49.439
- 10 km operating.
- The gun.

254
00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:50.822
You have five minutes.

255
00:16:50.823 --> 00:16:53.274
1.010 hectopascal.

256
00:16:53.275 --> 00:16:56.043
Few clouds at 1.200 feet.

257
00:17:02.234 --> 00:17:05.358
[4 minutes to the attack]

258
00:17:05.359 --> 00:17:06.359
Hi.

259
00:17:14.567 --> 00:17:15.765
Flower delivery?

260
00:17:20.817 --> 00:17:22.026
Who is it for?

261
00:17:22.027 --> 00:17:24.039
Do you want me to deliver it for you?

262
00:17:26.108 --> 00:17:28.234
- It's for you-know-who.
- Who?

263
00:17:33.585 --> 00:17:35.400
- Go away. Get lost.
- If you want...

264
00:17:35.401 --> 00:17:36.401
Get lost.

265
00:17:36.402 --> 00:17:39.275
I can deliver it when
you've made up your mind.

266
00:17:39.276 --> 00:17:41.691
Anyway. I'm here.

267
00:17:41.692 --> 00:17:42.844
I'm always here.

268
00:17:45.277 --> 00:17:46.652
Hey. you.

269
00:17:47.902 --> 00:17:50.067
Did you see Liu Peiqiang?

270
00:17:50.068 --> 00:17:51.152
Liu Peiqiang.

271
00:17:51.153 --> 00:17:52.153
No.

272
00:17:55.110 --> 00:17:56.110
Nov?

273
00:17:56.977 --> 00:17:58.692
Simultaneous interpretation online.

274
00:17:58.693 --> 00:18:00.688
You're dropping off new trainees too?

275
00:18:01.443 --> 00:18:03.151
Don't embarrass our school.

276
00:18:03.152 --> 00:18:06.337
You bastard. Call me by my full name.

277
00:18:07.860 --> 00:18:10.443
It has been years and we both lost weight.

278
00:18:10.444 --> 00:18:11.860
You don't look the same.

279
00:18:19.359 --> 00:18:20.692
What's going on?

280
00:18:20.693 --> 00:18:23.071
Don't close the door.
There's still someone else.

281
00:18:23.072 --> 00:18:24.152
Open the door.

282
00:18:24.153 --> 00:18:29.068
As the light of Earth.
I should've gone to the Moon last year.

283
00:18:29.069 --> 00:18:32.360
But they made me teach another batch.

284
00:18:32.361 --> 00:18:35.235
Mr. Wang is jealous of me.

285
00:18:35.236 --> 00:18:37.487
That's right. It's because
you're the light of Earth.

286
00:18:37.488 --> 00:18:39.653
I didn't do it on purpose.

287
00:18:40.991 --> 00:18:43.546
[Remove before flight]

288
00:18:46.194 --> 00:18:48.527
Who unplugged all the safety plugs?

289
00:18:48.528 --> 00:18:49.610
Who did this?

290
00:18:49.611 --> 00:18:51.820
I don't know. What the hell is happening?

291
00:18:58.778 --> 00:19:02.612
Mr. Wang is aiming at me.

292
00:19:06.654 --> 00:19:09.444
We lost control of all the drones!

293
00:19:09.445 --> 00:19:11.070
Our system has been hacked!

294
00:19:24.319 --> 00:19:26.201
We're going to work straight from here?

295
00:19:26.202 --> 00:19:27.663
Will we get overtime pay?

296
00:19:29.612 --> 00:19:33.153
Space Elevator Cabin 2
emergency launch initiated.

297
00:19:33.154 --> 00:19:35.611
All passengers be seated immediately.

298
00:19:35.612 --> 00:19:38.194
- I don't have an anti-G suit.
- Come on. hurry. This way.

299
00:19:38.195 --> 00:19:40.029
Please take safety precautions.

300
00:19:41.239 --> 00:19:45.326
[Joint Research Base Control Tower. Gabon]

301
00:19:46.905 --> 00:19:47.715
[Cabin-09 Ascending]

302
00:19:47.715 --> 00:19:48.316
[Cabin-08 Ascending]

303
00:19:48.316 --> 00:19:49.293
[Cabin-03 Ascending]

304
00:19:49.293 --> 00:19:50.041
[Cabin-01 Ascending]

305
00:19:50.042 --> 00:19:51.070
Five.

306
00:19:51.071 --> 00:19:52.195
- What's going on?
- Four.

307
00:19:52.196 --> 00:19:53.155
- All right.
- Don't mess around.

308
00:19:53.156 --> 00:19:54.654
- Three.
- Let's go.

309
00:19:54.655 --> 00:19:56.029
Two.

310
00:19:56.030 --> 00:19:57.404
- One.
- Let's go. everybody...

311
00:19:57.405 --> 00:19:58.405
Launch.

312
00:20:08.655 --> 00:20:10.237
[Warning]

313
00:20:10.238 --> 00:20:11.457
[Cabin-07 Ascending]
[Cabin-04 Ascending]

314
00:20:11.458 --> 00:20:13.058
[Cabin-06 Ascending]
[Cabin-02 Ascending]

315
00:20:18.238 --> 00:20:19.488
My God.

316
00:20:24.031 --> 00:20:25.031
Jeff.

317
00:20:25.032 --> 00:20:26.321
Is communication back up?

318
00:20:26.322 --> 00:20:28.988
Don't ask me. I also don't have any idea.

319
00:20:28.989 --> 00:20:32.113
Central Control. Do you read me?
[35 minutes to the Space Station crash]

320
00:20:32.114 --> 00:20:34.238
Central Control.

321
00:20:34.239 --> 00:20:35.821
Do you read me?

322
00:20:35.822 --> 00:20:37.405
Come in. Central Control.

323
00:20:37.406 --> 00:20:38.738
Can you hear me?

324
00:20:38.739 --> 00:20:41.117
Come in. Come in. Central Control.

325
00:20:41.118 --> 00:20:43.071
Control. Do you read me?

326
00:20:43.072 --> 00:20:44.247
The same exact name.

327
00:20:45.677 --> 00:20:47.239
[Han Duoduo]

328
00:20:48.364 --> 00:20:49.989
That's the same as my name.

329
00:20:50.655 --> 00:20:52.780
- They're reserve astronauts too?
- Which batch?

330
00:20:52.781 --> 00:20:55.364
- What does this mean?
- I haven't seen them.

331
00:21:02.614 --> 00:21:03.990
Hey. my foot is stuck!

332
00:21:18.907 --> 00:21:21.365
Air raid!

333
00:21:23.032 --> 00:21:23.948
Peiqiang!

334
00:21:23.949 --> 00:21:25.572
- Air raid warning!
- Peiqiang!

335
00:21:25.573 --> 00:21:30.114
Air raid warning!
All combat units. advance position now!

336
00:21:30.115 --> 00:21:32.038
Liu Peiqiang!

337
00:21:32.039 --> 00:21:33.289
You're fired.

338
00:21:34.615 --> 00:21:37.178
- I quit. so you can't fire me.
- What are you doing?

339
00:21:39.282 --> 00:21:40.657
I don't like quitters.

340
00:21:42.532 --> 00:21:43.709
Give it to her.

341
00:21:44.689 --> 00:21:45.803
Give her your name tag.

342
00:21:52.369 --> 00:21:54.494
Your flirting skills suck.

343
00:22:01.843 --> 00:22:04.198
[Locked]
[Enter emergency mode]

344
00:22:04.199 --> 00:22:06.407
All fighters. scramble.

345
00:22:06.408 --> 00:22:08.323
Annihilate all drones.

346
00:22:08.324 --> 00:22:09.948
Protect the Space Elevator
and test Earth Engines.

347
00:22:09.949 --> 00:22:11.823
Our system has been attacked!

348
00:22:11.824 --> 00:22:14.958
Alert Ground Control to initiate
Emergency Response Plan 5.

349
00:22:25.912 --> 00:22:27.408
The hack was a success.

350
00:22:27.409 --> 00:22:29.699
Drones are breaching their defense.

351
00:22:29.700 --> 00:22:31.491
We don't have much time.

352
00:22:31.492 --> 00:22:35.616
Approach from both sides
and leave nothing to chance.

353
00:22:35.617 --> 00:22:37.949
They are stealing identities.
Why only ours?

354
00:22:37.950 --> 00:22:39.824
How did they get in?

355
00:22:39.825 --> 00:22:41.284
Open the door first.

356
00:22:41.285 --> 00:22:44.491
Our ID gives them access to CIC.

357
00:22:44.492 --> 00:22:45.888
Their target is...

358
00:22:47.700 --> 00:22:49.242
the Ark Space Station.

359
00:22:51.624 --> 00:22:53.041
Calling Control Tower!

360
00:22:54.242 --> 00:22:55.824
I'm sorry.

361
00:22:55.825 --> 00:22:57.116
All communication is cut off.

362
00:22:57.117 --> 00:22:58.826
- All communication is cut off!
- Wake up!

363
00:22:58.827 --> 00:22:59.949
Let's go.

364
00:22:59.950 --> 00:23:01.242
You sit there!

365
00:23:01.243 --> 00:23:02.333
Don't move!

366
00:23:22.743 --> 00:23:23.967
Liu Peiqiang!

367
00:23:28.910 --> 00:23:30.826
You fool. let me out!

368
00:23:36.035 --> 00:23:37.035
Shut up!

369
00:23:38.368 --> 00:23:39.368
Let me out!

370
00:23:42.243 --> 00:23:44.076
I can't hear you!

371
00:23:46.036 --> 00:23:47.493
- Liu Peiqiang!
- Liu Peiqiang.

372
00:23:47.494 --> 00:23:48.911
You can't defeat them.

373
00:23:51.285 --> 00:23:53.035
We're not regularized yet.

374
00:23:53.036 --> 00:23:54.859
We don't have medical insurance.

375
00:23:56.368 --> 00:23:59.035
My earpiece is broken. I don't understand.

376
00:23:59.036 --> 00:24:00.660
But I get it.

377
00:24:00.661 --> 00:24:02.119
Even if I'm the only one left.

378
00:24:03.076 --> 00:24:04.701
I'll guard the Space Elevator with my life.

379
00:24:04.702 --> 00:24:06.951
It seems that you don't get it.

380
00:24:06.952 --> 00:24:09.786
What I mean is
we shouldn't have opened this door.

381
00:24:18.494 --> 00:24:23.168
All ordinance officers.
prepare ammunition for air-to-air combat.

382
00:24:23.169 --> 00:24:24.877
Air Defense Mode 1. got it!

383
00:24:25.578 --> 00:24:27.453
Remove the safety!

384
00:24:28.203 --> 00:24:31.243
I repeat. Don't forget
to turn off the safety.

385
00:24:56.619 --> 00:24:58.077
First launch.

386
00:24:58.078 --> 00:24:59.369
Target locking failed.

387
00:24:59.370 --> 00:25:00.287
Target locking failed.

388
00:25:00.288 --> 00:25:01.620
They're all fucking allies.

389
00:25:03.245 --> 00:25:05.495
I can't even tell who are the enemies.

390
00:25:05.496 --> 00:25:06.912
The ones on the radar are allies.

391
00:25:06.913 --> 00:25:08.787
Cut the crap.

392
00:25:08.788 --> 00:25:10.745
I'm locked as a target.

393
00:25:10.746 --> 00:25:12.578
I can't shake them off.

394
00:25:12.579 --> 00:25:14.453
Nov. shake them off now!

395
00:25:14.454 --> 00:25:16.703
I'm working on it.

396
00:25:16.704 --> 00:25:19.663
The sky is full of people.
Why only go after me?

397
00:25:43.246 --> 00:25:45.578
There are too many of them.
Too fucking many!

398
00:25:45.579 --> 00:25:48.704
Help! Mom. I want to go home!

399
00:25:48.705 --> 00:25:52.746
What should I do?

400
00:25:52.747 --> 00:25:55.163
The drones' vortex won't last long.

401
00:25:55.164 --> 00:25:57.913
You have a big fuel tank. Wear them out!

402
00:25:57.914 --> 00:25:59.329
Then what?

403
00:25:59.330 --> 00:26:01.371
Kovochur.

404
00:26:01.372 --> 00:26:02.579
God!

405
00:26:02.580 --> 00:26:06.622
Ura!

406
00:26:07.289 --> 00:26:10.996
I was the best in school for a reason.

407
00:26:10.997 --> 00:26:12.872
Stop showing off. Backup is here.

408
00:26:15.747 --> 00:26:17.247
I shook them off!

409
00:26:18.122 --> 00:26:20.413
Daddy is back!

410
00:26:20.414 --> 00:26:23.121
Visual attack.

411
00:26:23.122 --> 00:26:24.122
Kill them!

412
00:26:34.580 --> 00:26:37.414
How long will it take
for the command system to come back again?

413
00:26:37.415 --> 00:26:38.914
Go to the base station.

414
00:26:38.915 --> 00:26:41.497
Connect 550C to the system.

415
00:26:41.498 --> 00:26:42.498
Move!

416
00:26:47.436 --> 00:26:50.539
[Joint Research Base UCAV
Control Center. Gabon]

417
00:26:50.540 --> 00:26:52.455
Our system has been breached.

418
00:26:52.456 --> 00:26:54.830
Connect 550C to the communication network.

419
00:26:54.831 --> 00:26:56.414
Overwrite the system.

420
00:26:56.415 --> 00:26:58.997
If we can successfully overwrite the 550C.
[Intelligent Quantum Computer 550C]

421
00:26:58.998 --> 00:27:00.372
we can regain control.

422
00:27:00.373 --> 00:27:02.539
Attention. all units.

423
00:27:02.540 --> 00:27:04.831
Unidentified object
approaching at high speed!

424
00:27:06.832 --> 00:27:08.624
Missiles!

425
00:27:08.625 --> 00:27:10.015
What the fuck are these?

426
00:27:15.373 --> 00:27:18.706
Their target is the Space Elevator!

427
00:27:18.707 --> 00:27:20.998
Cut the crap!
Use the tactic Mr. Wang taught us.

428
00:27:20.999 --> 00:27:22.416
Go! I'll cover you.

429
00:27:26.916 --> 00:27:27.916
Launch two.

430
00:27:37.718 --> 00:27:40.041
Hurry. Stop him! He's getting the remote.

431
00:27:47.542 --> 00:27:49.667
SEV-09 signal lost.
[Cabin-09 signal lost]

432
00:27:59.292 --> 00:28:01.833
Left wing damaged!

433
00:28:06.292 --> 00:28:08.582
Bomb! Someone just dropped!

434
00:28:08.583 --> 00:28:10.167
Someone just dropped!

435
00:28:11.666 --> 00:28:15.124
They want to destroy
all the elevator cabins!

436
00:28:15.125 --> 00:28:17.208
Nov. we can't catch up to them.

437
00:28:19.416 --> 00:28:21.332
It's okay. I'm faster than you.

438
00:28:21.333 --> 00:28:23.291
Requesting backup!

439
00:28:23.292 --> 00:28:25.417
Higher! Stronger!

440
00:28:42.418 --> 00:28:43.376
Let go.

441
00:28:43.377 --> 00:28:44.751
You let go first.

442
00:29:14.876 --> 00:29:17.794
Cabin 4 just got...

443
00:29:19.585 --> 00:29:24.293
granted the access at the space station.

444
00:29:24.294 --> 00:29:26.668
We're the only ones who
passed the identity checks.

445
00:29:26.669 --> 00:29:28.043
Reaching target height.

446
00:29:28.044 --> 00:29:29.293
Ready to detonate.

447
00:29:29.294 --> 00:29:30.709
Pass granted.

448
00:29:30.710 --> 00:29:34.001
Passage through Cargo
Transfer Area granted.

449
00:29:34.002 --> 00:29:38.543
Welcome to Docking Area A3
of the Ark Space Station.

450
00:29:38.544 --> 00:29:40.627
We wish you a good day.

451
00:29:51.335 --> 00:29:54.085
550C system scan complete.

452
00:29:54.086 --> 00:29:56.752
Real-time system overwrite complete.

453
00:29:56.753 --> 00:29:58.460
Drone control attained.

454
00:29:58.461 --> 00:29:59.461
Now.

455
00:30:02.294 --> 00:30:05.085
The 550C is taking over
control of all drones.

456
00:30:05.086 --> 00:30:08.253
Power system shut down with override.

457
00:30:21.586 --> 00:30:22.503
Awesome!

458
00:30:22.504 --> 00:30:24.295
Hoorah!

459
00:30:26.003 --> 00:30:28.212
550C is so fast.

460
00:30:29.671 --> 00:30:32.712
Real-time overwrite of
the Space Elevator system completed.

461
00:30:33.378 --> 00:30:35.295
Space Elevator control regained!

462
00:30:35.296 --> 00:30:37.170
Abort launch process!

463
00:30:37.171 --> 00:30:39.711
Initiate elevator cabin return thruster!

464
00:30:39.712 --> 00:30:40.847
Injecting Water.

465
00:30:40.848 --> 00:30:41.961
Ice shield.

466
00:30:41.962 --> 00:30:42.962
Commence.

467
00:30:47.671 --> 00:30:49.378
Attention.

468
00:30:49.379 --> 00:30:52.128
All reserve astronauts in Cabin 2.

469
00:30:52.129 --> 00:30:55.140
The cabin has been
targeted by suicide drones.

470
00:30:55.141 --> 00:30:57.699
Detonation must be stopped at all cost.

471
00:30:58.586 --> 00:31:00.187
Attention.

472
00:31:00.188 --> 00:31:02.961
All reserve astronauts in Cabin 2.

473
00:31:02.962 --> 00:31:05.878
The cabin has been
targeted by suicide drones.

474
00:31:05.879 --> 00:31:08.309
Detonation must be stopped at all cost.

475
00:31:32.588 --> 00:31:33.837
My finger.

476
00:31:33.838 --> 00:31:34.838
Duoduo!

477
00:31:38.922 --> 00:31:40.297
Liu Peiqiang!

478
00:31:59.963 --> 00:32:02.713
The Space Elevator must be destroyed.

479
00:32:02.714 --> 00:32:03.838
Go. Duoduo!

480
00:32:03.839 --> 00:32:08.298
Digital Life is the only way out!

481
00:32:09.798 --> 00:32:13.172
- In another world.
- You ruined...

482
00:32:13.173 --> 00:32:14.506
we'll live...

483
00:32:15.381 --> 00:32:18.839
- forever!
- My flowers!

484
00:32:22.173 --> 00:32:23.420
I'll kill you!

485
00:32:24.464 --> 00:32:25.839
Stand up!

486
00:32:28.006 --> 00:32:29.218
Stand!

487
00:32:32.840 --> 00:32:34.241
What are you looking at?

488
00:32:37.257 --> 00:32:38.483
Give me the flowers.

489
00:32:52.090 --> 00:32:53.214
Duoduo.

490
00:32:53.215 --> 00:32:54.132
The flower.

491
00:32:54.133 --> 00:32:55.465
- Get lost.
- Okay.

492
00:32:59.424 --> 00:33:01.048
Kill me.

493
00:33:01.049 --> 00:33:05.089
- I don't want to live in this world.
- Authorization reclaimed for seven elevator cabs.

494
00:33:05.090 --> 00:33:08.381
- Elevators No. 1. 2. and 5 are returning.
- Put your hands up slowly.

495
00:33:08.382 --> 00:33:10.466
- Ground unit. get ready to aid.
- Hand it over.

496
00:33:24.550 --> 00:33:25.758
Holy shit!

497
00:33:35.465 --> 00:33:36.590
What's going on?

498
00:33:36.591 --> 00:33:39.091
Look at the sky. It's on fire!

499
00:34:33.510 --> 00:34:35.010
The Space Station has fallen.

500
00:34:37.384 --> 00:34:38.884
I repeat.

501
00:34:38.885 --> 00:34:40.769
The Space Station has fallen.

502
00:34:56.343 --> 00:34:58.302
Herbert. Are you okay?

503
00:35:00.760 --> 00:35:01.760
Help me.

504
00:35:01.761 --> 00:35:03.259
Help me.

505
00:35:03.260 --> 00:35:05.178
- Move aside.
- Nurse.

506
00:35:18.489 --> 00:35:25.106
[Joint Research Base 2nd
Central Hospital. Gabon]

507
00:35:31.468 --> 00:35:33.135
Mr. Secretary.

508
00:35:33.136 --> 00:35:34.344
Ladies and gentlemen.

509
00:35:36.386 --> 00:35:38.260
Merely four hours ago.

510
00:35:38.261 --> 00:35:43.178
the Space Elevator suffered a carefully
planned and organized terrorist attack.

511
00:35:44.594 --> 00:35:49.969
As of now. the death toll stands at 3.521.

512
00:35:49.970 --> 00:35:53.513
with a further 5.137 injured.

513
00:35:54.679 --> 00:35:58.719
This is the largest terrorist attack
aimed at the Moving Mountain Project

514
00:35:58.720 --> 00:36:02.470
since the attack on the UEG headquarters
three months ago.

515
00:36:03.679 --> 00:36:09.761
This attack has directly caused severe
delays in the Moving Mountain Project.

516
00:36:09.762 --> 00:36:13.053
This means we will not be
able to complete in time

517
00:36:13.054 --> 00:36:16.345
the verification of the
feasibility of these projects.

518
00:36:17.179 --> 00:36:20.344
Mankind's countermeasures
against the Solar Crisis

519
00:36:20.345 --> 00:36:23.430
are increasingly likely to be terminated.

520
00:36:24.679 --> 00:36:29.136
We reserve all rights
to take further action as appropriate.

521
00:36:29.137 --> 00:36:35.387
We are confident in our ability to protect
our homeland and the safety of our citizens.

522
00:36:35.388 --> 00:36:36.869
[7 months to the first ignition]

523
00:36:45.930 --> 00:36:47.263
The Space Agency replied.

524
00:36:47.264 --> 00:36:48.924
We still have a seven-month window.

525
00:36:53.096 --> 00:36:54.263
Seven months.

526
00:36:57.221 --> 00:36:58.221
Xiaoxi.

527
00:37:04.138 --> 00:37:05.138
Mr. Zhou.

528
00:37:07.430 --> 00:37:10.888
You want me to make such
an important statement?

529
00:37:17.806 --> 00:37:20.306
Is there ever an
unimportant statement here?

530
00:37:21.389 --> 00:37:24.722
Just read it word for word.

531
00:37:35.931 --> 00:37:39.432
The Space Elevator was destroyed
in an attack on March 12th.

532
00:37:39.433 --> 00:37:42.349
The Moving Mountain Project
is facing a major setback.

533
00:37:43.222 --> 00:37:47.388
Protests broke out in many places
asking to restart the Digital Life Project.

534
00:37:47.389 --> 00:37:49.806
I live forever!

535
00:37:50.888 --> 00:37:52.306
Due to time pressure.

536
00:37:52.307 --> 00:37:56.798
UEG held an emergency conference to discuss
the relaunch of the Digital Life Project.

537
00:37:56.799 --> 00:38:00.639
We'll continue to firmly
implement the existing plan.

538
00:38:00.640 --> 00:38:02.182
Within seven months.

539
00:38:02.183 --> 00:38:04.891
we'll complete the Moving Mountain Project
feasibility test.

540
00:38:05.807 --> 00:38:07.722
What's going on?

541
00:38:07.723 --> 00:38:10.431
What's happening?

542
00:38:10.432 --> 00:38:12.182
What the hell is going on?

543
00:38:12.183 --> 00:38:14.266
- Quick.
- Our electricity system has been hacked.

544
00:38:15.847 --> 00:38:18.014
We call on all countries to
manage their differences.

545
00:38:18.015 --> 00:38:20.972
Simultaneous interpretation is online.

546
00:38:20.973 --> 00:38:22.431
stop preparing for war.

547
00:38:22.432 --> 00:38:26.807
Put more effort into the
Solar Crisis initiatives.

548
00:38:28.066 --> 00:38:31.840
The main artery that links Earth
and the Moon has been cut.

549
00:38:33.016 --> 00:38:36.505
We underestimated the
opposition's power to infiltrate.

550
00:38:39.141 --> 00:38:43.672
91% of Americans do not believe
in the Moving Mountain Project.

551
00:38:43.673 --> 00:38:49.174
The US Senate is discussing pulling out of
it and restarting the Digital Life Project.

552
00:38:50.682 --> 00:38:52.765
More are questioning

553
00:38:52.766 --> 00:38:58.932
how much solving a crisis 100 years in the
future should matter to people living now.

554
00:38:58.933 --> 00:39:02.516
It seems the world isn't
on the side of reality.

555
00:39:03.765 --> 00:39:04.765
Zhou.

556
00:39:06.141 --> 00:39:08.309
What do you think we should do now?

557
00:39:22.392 --> 00:39:24.699
Let me show you something.

558
00:39:27.892 --> 00:39:28.892
What is it?

559
00:39:32.649 --> 00:39:34.066
- That?
- Right here.

560
00:39:34.725 --> 00:39:35.809
In 1990.

561
00:39:37.017 --> 00:39:42.891
your Voyager took this photo of Earth.

562
00:39:42.892 --> 00:39:43.892
Right.

563
00:39:45.267 --> 00:39:47.684
This little white dot...

564
00:39:48.559 --> 00:39:50.475
is our everything.

565
00:39:51.225 --> 00:39:53.176
The Moving Mountain Project...

566
00:39:53.893 --> 00:39:59.393
would like to build 10.000 engines
in this little white dot...

567
00:40:00.351 --> 00:40:05.810
and take them to a new
home 2.500 years from now.

568
00:40:08.601 --> 00:40:11.268
Mike. do you believe that?

569
00:40:15.643 --> 00:40:20.143
That's just a photo from space
that's Voyager looking back at us.

570
00:40:22.268 --> 00:40:23.768
I believe it.

571
00:40:27.060 --> 00:40:29.518
My children will believe it.

572
00:40:30.518 --> 00:40:33.144
My children's children will believe it.

573
00:40:35.102 --> 00:40:36.769
By then.

574
00:40:37.976 --> 00:40:41.601
I believe that we'll see the blue sky

575
00:40:41.602 --> 00:40:44.811
and branches full of flowers again.

576
00:40:50.061 --> 00:40:51.311
Next.

577
00:40:52.352 --> 00:40:55.061
what do you think you should do?

578
00:40:59.519 --> 00:41:01.477
I'll convey this to my president.

579
00:41:03.490 --> 00:41:04.903
By the way.

580
00:41:04.904 --> 00:41:08.122
completing the feasibility test
for the Moving Mountain Project

581
00:41:08.123 --> 00:41:11.685
in just seven months is quite doubtful.

582
00:41:11.686 --> 00:41:12.894
But good luck.

583
00:41:16.228 --> 00:41:17.228
Seven months.

584
00:41:19.312 --> 00:41:20.478
Two engines.

585
00:41:21.228 --> 00:41:22.395
Only us.

586
00:41:23.103 --> 00:41:24.103
That's not fair.

587
00:41:25.062 --> 00:41:26.187
Xiaoxi.

588
00:41:27.228 --> 00:41:29.852
If everything is fair.

589
00:41:29.853 --> 00:41:32.312
why build this building?

590
00:41:33.145 --> 00:41:35.145
In the face of crisis.

591
00:41:35.146 --> 00:41:37.104
only responsibility exists.

592
00:41:39.478 --> 00:41:42.353
Unity comes with a price.

593
00:41:50.595 --> 00:41:53.262
The first batch of supplies is on the way.

594
00:41:55.229 --> 00:41:58.397
We're counting on them
for the next seven months.

595
00:42:22.146 --> 00:42:25.978
[Tu Hengyu]

596
00:42:25.979 --> 00:42:27.603
Dad.

597
00:42:27.604 --> 00:42:29.604
How do I solve this?

598
00:42:39.980 --> 00:42:45.975
[Campanus]

599
00:42:46.630 --> 00:42:49.313
The solar storm destroyed Transformer 4.

600
00:42:49.314 --> 00:42:52.021
The electricity is out.
what do you want me to do?

601
00:42:52.022 --> 00:42:55.271
We need to pull everyone
out before they suffocate.

602
00:42:55.272 --> 00:42:57.264
This is the fourth time this month.

603
00:42:59.979 --> 00:43:01.354
Stop your whining.

604
00:43:01.355 --> 00:43:03.771
The solar activity is about to burst.

605
00:43:03.772 --> 00:43:05.154
Better get used to it.

606
00:43:10.730 --> 00:43:12.530
[Emergency awakening]
[Life support power off]

607
00:43:49.992 --> 00:43:55.766
[Intelligent Quantum Computer 550A]

608
00:44:18.399 --> 00:44:19.399
Dad.

609
00:44:20.857 --> 00:44:23.149
It's so dark over there. Dad.

610
00:44:24.039 --> 00:44:25.191
It's okay.

611
00:44:25.192 --> 00:44:27.108
It's fine. Our power is out.

612
00:44:28.149 --> 00:44:29.305
Dad.

613
00:44:31.024 --> 00:44:33.649
Dad. how do I solve this?

614
00:44:35.942 --> 00:44:39.018
This is too hard. I don't
know how to solve it.

615
00:44:40.692 --> 00:44:43.025
Then teach me how to braid my hair.

616
00:44:45.774 --> 00:44:47.899
Tu Hengyu. the last batch
of supplies has arrived.

617
00:44:47.900 --> 00:44:49.566
Come out to assemble now.

618
00:44:49.567 --> 00:44:50.483
Dad.

619
00:44:50.484 --> 00:44:52.357
Dad. I want a hug!

620
00:44:52.358 --> 00:44:54.275
I'll hug you when I'm back. okay?

621
00:44:56.775 --> 00:44:57.982
Ma Zhao.

622
00:44:57.983 --> 00:45:00.191
I'll find a chance to show you
[UEC Joint Research Base. Campanus]

623
00:45:00.192 --> 00:45:02.478
the return capsule from
our first lunar mission.

624
00:45:03.188 --> 00:45:07.983
Apart from me. that's the
second light of Earth.

625
00:45:22.734 --> 00:45:25.858
Seven months correspond to the next solar
maxima. [3 months to the first ignition]

626
00:45:25.859 --> 00:45:28.400
The solar wind is detrimental
to electronic equipment.

627
00:45:28.401 --> 00:45:30.983
We can't work on the lunar surface
for at least a year.

628
00:45:30.984 --> 00:45:34.733
Before this. we must ignite
the lunar satellite engine

629
00:45:34.734 --> 00:45:36.900
and give the world an answer.

630
00:45:36.901 --> 00:45:41.900
They brought us new equipment
to help us complete the engine test.

631
00:45:41.901 --> 00:45:43.442
Mr. Ma.

632
00:45:43.443 --> 00:45:44.651
Say a few words.

633
00:45:46.443 --> 00:45:48.377
Come on. give a round of applause.

634
00:45:54.775 --> 00:45:56.109
This is 550C.

635
00:45:56.110 --> 00:45:58.235
the most advanced self-sensing.
self-adapting. self-organizing.

636
00:45:58.236 --> 00:46:00.526
and remoldable compiling compute core.

637
00:46:00.527 --> 00:46:01.658
After connecting to the hardware.

638
00:46:01.659 --> 00:46:03.401
it can generate an underlying
operating system in real-time

639
00:46:03.402 --> 00:46:05.526
and automatically organize
engine construction.

640
00:46:05.527 --> 00:46:07.359
There are currently
three of these worldwide.

641
00:46:07.360 --> 00:46:10.069
To collect automated data.
we brought this one here.

642
00:46:10.070 --> 00:46:13.472
[Light of the Earth Lunar Module. Campanus]
[Russia's First Moon Landing Module]

643
00:46:17.319 --> 00:46:21.859
Tu Hengyu and I are responsible
for 550C's system operation.

644
00:46:21.860 --> 00:46:22.860
Okay. Mr. Ma.

645
00:46:28.444 --> 00:46:31.840
I believe that with its help. we can quickly
recover from the solar wind's impact

646
00:46:31.841 --> 00:46:33.870
and guarantee the ignition test's launch.

647
00:46:38.070 --> 00:46:44.235
[The Moving Mountain Project]
[01 Test Lunar Engine]

648
00:46:44.236 --> 00:46:46.819
Tu Hengyu. connect 500C
as soon as possible.

649
00:46:46.820 --> 00:46:49.527
Test its compatibility and
restart damaged modules.

650
00:46:49.528 --> 00:46:52.085
Mr. Ma. you must enter your password.

651
00:47:13.820 --> 00:47:15.695
[Engineering machine modules
activated successfully]

652
00:47:15.696 --> 00:47:17.530
Module Group 11 activated.

653
00:47:20.237 --> 00:47:22.196
Module Group 27 activated.

654
00:47:23.946 --> 00:47:25.737
Module Group 31 activated.

655
00:47:27.529 --> 00:47:29.321
Module Group 44 activated.

656
00:47:32.987 --> 00:47:35.695
DOG Cluster activated.

657
00:47:35.696 --> 00:47:37.416
Printing of construction materials resumed.

658
00:47:40.696 --> 00:47:42.279
550C is so fast.

659
00:47:47.237 --> 00:47:48.821
Its speed is so fast.

660
00:47:54.737 --> 00:47:56.988
I brought your data card from our center.

661
00:48:02.113 --> 00:48:04.946
This is the backup when
you just got back in 2037.

662
00:48:04.947 --> 00:48:06.654
This concerns personal privacy.

663
00:48:06.655 --> 00:48:08.946
After our center shuts down.
all participants must decide

664
00:48:08.947 --> 00:48:10.822
if they want to keep a personal backup.

665
00:48:10.823 --> 00:48:12.823
If you want it. sign here.

666
00:48:14.697 --> 00:48:16.572
If not. I'll destroy it in front of you.

667
00:48:20.696 --> 00:48:21.904
Where's your backup?

668
00:48:21.905 --> 00:48:23.237
I didn't keep one.

669
00:48:23.238 --> 00:48:26.948
I hope that I can truly die someday
and not become someone's digital pet.

670
00:48:29.655 --> 00:48:32.404
When we're dead. we're dead.
That's the reality.

671
00:48:32.405 --> 00:48:35.987
There's a level Z3 solar storm forecast
arriving in four hours.

672
00:48:35.988 --> 00:48:38.280
I know what you're thinking.

673
00:48:38.281 --> 00:48:41.363
In the next three months.
we must work day and night.

674
00:48:41.364 --> 00:48:43.947
If the lunar satellite
engine ignition test fails.

675
00:48:43.948 --> 00:48:45.114
we'll all die.

676
00:48:51.864 --> 00:48:52.864
Dad.

677
00:48:53.823 --> 00:48:56.364
Dad. how do I solve this?

678
00:48:58.823 --> 00:49:02.566
This is too hard. I don't
know how to solve it.

679
00:49:04.531 --> 00:49:07.280
Then teach me how to braid my hair.

680
00:49:07.281 --> 00:49:08.281
Sure.

681
00:49:10.114 --> 00:49:11.613
Mr. Ma.

682
00:49:11.614 --> 00:49:14.198
Dad. you're with Mr. Ma?

683
00:49:18.789 --> 00:49:19.789
Follow this.

684
00:49:20.824 --> 00:49:23.781
Mr. Ma. what are you doing?

685
00:49:23.782 --> 00:49:24.782
Yaya.

686
00:49:25.532 --> 00:49:26.824
I have to work.

687
00:49:27.698 --> 00:49:29.239
Go get some rest.

688
00:49:29.240 --> 00:49:31.532
Bye. Dad. Bye. Mr. Ma.

689
00:49:37.316 --> 00:49:39.616
Dad. where is this place?

690
00:49:40.289 --> 00:49:41.414
Where's Mom?

691
00:49:44.407 --> 00:49:47.624
Dad. it's so cold here.
I want a hug from you.

692
00:49:50.407 --> 00:49:53.157
Dad. where's Mom?

693
00:49:53.949 --> 00:49:56.157
Dad. hug me!

694
00:50:00.158 --> 00:50:01.158
Dad.

695
00:50:02.741 --> 00:50:04.616
Dad. how do I solve this?

696
00:50:08.158 --> 00:50:11.033
In which generation was
self-awareness developed?

697
00:50:11.034 --> 00:50:12.387
The 425th.

698
00:50:14.366 --> 00:50:17.199
This is the real hope
of digital life research and development.

699
00:50:17.200 --> 00:50:18.840
Has our center's research...

700
00:50:20.283 --> 00:50:22.075
really stopped completely?

701
00:50:23.241 --> 00:50:24.741
Not completely.

702
00:50:24.742 --> 00:50:26.801
but permanently banned in the legal sense.

703
00:50:28.115 --> 00:50:30.532
If this technology becomes widespread
in this catastrophic time.

704
00:50:30.533 --> 00:50:32.903
no one will be willing to
live in the real world.

705
00:50:33.801 --> 00:50:35.893
After all. the temptation
of living forever in the digital world

706
00:50:35.894 --> 00:50:38.145
is too irresistible for ordinary people.

707
00:50:40.326 --> 00:50:43.575
â™« Twinkle. twinkle little star â™«

708
00:50:43.576 --> 00:50:47.325
â™« How I wonder what you are â™«

709
00:50:47.326 --> 00:50:48.908
Dad.

710
00:50:48.909 --> 00:50:51.908
I want to have ice cream
first in the amusement park.

711
00:50:51.909 --> 00:50:54.158
Do you want strawberry or milk flavor?

712
00:50:54.159 --> 00:50:56.700
I want the biggest one. the
one that's bigger than me.

713
00:50:56.701 --> 00:50:57.991
Have one of each.

714
00:50:57.992 --> 00:51:00.908
Your mom is the one
who always eats them in the end.

715
00:51:00.909 --> 00:51:02.991
All my teeth will fall out.

716
00:51:02.992 --> 00:51:04.616
- Will that be okay?
- When we get there.

717
00:51:04.617 --> 00:51:05.865
I'll buy it for you.

718
00:51:36.660 --> 00:51:38.826
Are you crazy?
Why didn't you bring them to the hospital?

719
00:51:38.827 --> 00:51:40.555
- This isn't a hospital.
- She was brought here from the hospital.

720
00:51:40.556 --> 00:51:42.617
Mr. Ma. I don't dare to sign this.

721
00:51:42.618 --> 00:51:44.409
These are the center's equipment.

722
00:51:44.410 --> 00:51:46.409
I'm sorry to see Yaya this way.

723
00:51:46.410 --> 00:51:48.867
Her life is hanging by a thread.
This is an opportunity.

724
00:51:48.868 --> 00:51:50.410
This technology isn't mature yet.

725
00:51:51.117 --> 00:51:52.534
His wife is already dead.

726
00:51:52.535 --> 00:51:54.617
- Can't we keep some memories for the kid's dad?
- Mr. Ma.

727
00:51:54.618 --> 00:51:56.330
Who will take responsibility for this?

728
00:51:57.250 --> 00:51:58.250
I will.

729
00:52:18.368 --> 00:52:21.203
We're only one step away from
completing the research. Mr. Ma.

730
00:52:21.953 --> 00:52:25.703
550C's hardware has reached its limit.

731
00:52:26.569 --> 00:52:30.452
Yaya has iterated 915 generations so far.

732
00:52:30.453 --> 00:52:32.627
but she still only has two minutes to live.

733
00:52:36.536 --> 00:52:37.536
I want...

734
00:52:43.329 --> 00:52:44.329
I want...

735
00:52:46.787 --> 00:52:48.329
to give her a complete life.

736
00:52:52.787 --> 00:52:54.495
I know why you're showing me these.

737
00:52:55.662 --> 00:52:56.662
but no.

738
00:52:57.579 --> 00:53:00.286
550C can only be used
for the ignition test.

739
00:53:00.287 --> 00:53:02.579
After it's done. 550A will be recovered
and destroyed too.

740
00:53:03.662 --> 00:53:06.496
I allowed you to use 550A
before out of sympathy.

741
00:53:06.497 --> 00:53:07.746
Don't push it.

742
00:53:19.704 --> 00:53:21.079
Warning!

743
00:53:21.080 --> 00:53:23.204
Level Z9 solar storm.

744
00:53:23.205 --> 00:53:24.912
Warning!

745
00:53:24.913 --> 00:53:26.830
Level Z9 solar storm.

746
00:53:29.612 --> 00:53:32.204
[Joint Research Base No.21
Ming Field. Campanus]

747
00:53:32.205 --> 00:53:34.204
Attention. everyone!

748
00:53:34.205 --> 00:53:36.870
The solar storm will hit the lunar surface
in six minutes.

749
00:53:36.871 --> 00:53:39.081
- Stop working at once.
- Return to the base.

750
00:53:39.955 --> 00:53:41.995
Is this forecast true?

751
00:53:41.996 --> 00:53:42.996
Speed up.

752
00:53:42.997 --> 00:53:45.247
I thought we had another hour.

753
00:53:54.621 --> 00:53:56.287
Mr. Ma. Xiaoyu. where are you?

754
00:53:56.288 --> 00:53:57.993
The solar storm will hit the lunar surface
earlier than expected.

755
00:53:57.994 --> 00:53:59.537
Warning failure.

756
00:53:59.538 --> 00:54:02.038
There's 3 km. We still have 3 km to go.

757
00:54:02.039 --> 00:54:03.706
There's an underground bunker at the base.

758
00:54:03.707 --> 00:54:05.308
550C will only be safe there.

759
00:54:09.206 --> 00:54:11.163
This lousy vehicle is harder
to drive than a plane.

760
00:54:11.164 --> 00:54:13.830
Our life is more important.
Cut the crap. drive!

761
00:54:13.831 --> 00:54:16.622
The solar storm is about to hit us.

762
00:54:18.289 --> 00:54:20.205
We'll be there soon.

763
00:54:20.206 --> 00:54:22.456
Come out to unload!

764
00:54:29.038 --> 00:54:30.330
Inform Earth.

765
00:54:30.331 --> 00:54:33.538
A giant solar storm is
exceeding the forecasted level.

766
00:54:33.539 --> 00:54:36.205
That's nonsense. All communications
are cut off. How can we inform them?

767
00:54:36.206 --> 00:54:37.206
Hurry!

768
00:54:41.582 --> 00:54:42.540
Tu Hengyu.

769
00:54:42.541 --> 00:54:43.872
Hurry!

770
00:54:43.873 --> 00:54:45.832
Mr. Ma. the safety buckle is broken.

771
00:54:46.623 --> 00:54:48.082
Why must it be broken now?

772
00:54:51.582 --> 00:54:52.915
Go.

773
00:55:01.540 --> 00:55:03.206
There's not enough time. Let's go!

774
00:55:03.207 --> 00:55:04.789
If the oxygen supply is
broken. we'll all suffocate.

775
00:55:04.790 --> 00:55:06.247
We're almost there.

776
00:55:06.248 --> 00:55:07.665
Almost there.

777
00:55:12.248 --> 00:55:14.539
Tu Hengyu. hurry!

778
00:55:14.540 --> 00:55:15.699
Come on.

779
00:55:37.124 --> 00:55:39.915
Remove his helmet. The oxygen
supply is cut off. Hurry!

780
00:55:39.916 --> 00:55:42.499
He's suffocating. He's dying! Hurry!

781
00:55:51.666 --> 00:55:53.124
We're all still breathing.

782
00:55:57.083 --> 00:55:58.208
Jesus!

783
00:56:06.625 --> 00:56:07.750
Nice.

784
00:56:13.584 --> 00:56:15.500
The situation now...

785
00:56:17.750 --> 00:56:19.584
Right. this is the situation.

786
00:56:21.417 --> 00:56:24.959
What's strange is that none of our warning
devices... [3 days to the first ignition]

787
00:56:26.833 --> 00:56:28.749
sent out any warnings.

788
00:56:28.750 --> 00:56:30.874
550C is totally destroyed.

789
00:56:30.875 --> 00:56:34.500
Without it. we can't accurately
control the engine's launch position.

790
00:56:36.667 --> 00:56:37.917
If we forcefully ignite it...

791
00:56:39.834 --> 00:56:41.250
I'll smack you.

792
00:56:41.251 --> 00:56:44.209
The test is in three days.
If we miss the window. we're all doomed.

793
00:56:44.210 --> 00:56:45.484
You're all out of ideas?

794
00:56:48.918 --> 00:56:51.210
When will the safety buckle be safe?

795
00:56:58.085 --> 00:56:59.626
I have an idea.

796
00:57:01.085 --> 00:57:03.376
550A might work.

797
00:57:05.251 --> 00:57:06.501
Dad.

798
00:57:09.168 --> 00:57:11.751
Dad. how do I solve this?

799
00:57:14.668 --> 00:57:15.710
Write four.

800
00:57:16.710 --> 00:57:18.042
Write four.

801
00:57:18.043 --> 00:57:20.542
You're incredible. Dad!

802
00:57:20.543 --> 00:57:22.293
Yaya. be good.

803
00:57:22.294 --> 00:57:23.709
I'll be back to see you.

804
00:57:24.669 --> 00:57:25.669
Bye.

805
00:57:25.670 --> 00:57:27.044
Bye. Dad.

806
00:57:31.802 --> 00:57:33.415
Take it.

807
00:57:33.416 --> 00:57:35.336
It should be enough for ignition.

808
00:57:37.919 --> 00:57:41.460
I must spend a few days to modify it. But
the ignition's computational load is heavy.

809
00:57:41.461 --> 00:57:42.794
550A will be burned up.

810
00:57:42.795 --> 00:57:44.264
That's why I have a condition.

811
00:57:45.252 --> 00:57:47.475
Include me in the 550
series' further development.

812
00:57:50.669 --> 00:57:53.627
If you agree. I'll give
you 550A's password.

813
00:58:02.670 --> 00:58:04.252
Moving Mountain Project verification.

814
00:58:04.253 --> 00:58:08.337
Lunar satellite 1 test engine.
first ignition test begins.

815
00:58:09.587 --> 00:58:11.752
550A connects to the ignition module.

816
00:58:11.753 --> 00:58:13.086
Begin self-compilation.

817
00:58:13.087 --> 00:58:14.627
Begin synchronized overwrite.

818
00:58:14.628 --> 00:58:15.545
Copy.

819
00:58:15.546 --> 00:58:17.795
Attention. ignition unit.
Start the ignition.

820
00:58:19.462 --> 00:58:21.420
Helium-3 is loaded.

821
00:58:47.921 --> 00:58:49.253
Lighter loading completed.

822
00:58:49.254 --> 00:58:51.128
Underlying operating system generated.

823
00:58:51.129 --> 00:58:53.920
Begin the countdown to ignition.
All personnel. evacuate now.

824
00:58:53.921 --> 00:58:55.920
Mr. Ma. Hengyu. evacuate too.

825
00:58:55.921 --> 00:58:58.295
Tu Hengyu. what are you waiting for?

826
00:58:58.296 --> 00:58:59.296
Mr. Ma.

827
00:59:00.096 --> 00:59:02.338
I need to confirm what you promised me.

828
00:59:03.838 --> 00:59:05.643
This is very important to me.

829
00:59:07.463 --> 00:59:08.846
I want to give Yaya...

830
00:59:10.254 --> 00:59:11.504
a complete life.

831
00:59:13.046 --> 00:59:15.628
For the sake of Mother Earth!

832
00:59:15.629 --> 00:59:16.795
What are you doing?

833
00:59:16.796 --> 00:59:18.587
Hurry!

834
00:59:18.588 --> 00:59:20.129
Or we'll go ahead.

835
00:59:26.422 --> 00:59:27.422
I'm confirming it.

836
00:59:34.589 --> 00:59:37.672
If we succeed. don't forget about Yaya.

837
01:00:13.048 --> 01:00:15.465
Lunar 1 test engine ignition completed.

838
01:00:16.256 --> 01:00:20.006
The Moon successfully had an angular
displacement of 0.4 nano arc seconds.

839
01:00:20.964 --> 01:00:26.130
This proves the Moon could be pushed
to the target position within 20 years.

840
01:00:26.131 --> 01:00:29.208
- Come here and watch it.
- And remove its gravitational grip on Earth.

841
01:00:30.173 --> 01:00:32.839
Based on this achievement.

842
01:00:32.840 --> 01:00:37.340
Earth Engine 1 will begin
its trial ignition today.

843
01:00:38.340 --> 01:00:40.964
If we can successfully shift Earth as well.

844
01:00:40.965 --> 01:00:46.423
the two experiments will completely verify
the Moving Mountain Project's feasibility.

845
01:00:46.424 --> 01:00:52.506
And it will bring real hope to all mankind
in resolving the Solar Crisis.

846
01:00:52.507 --> 01:00:57.715
Ten. nine. eight. seven. six.

847
01:00:57.716 --> 01:00:58.716
five.

848
01:00:58.717 --> 01:00:59.840
four.

849
01:00:59.841 --> 01:01:00.923
three.

850
01:01:00.924 --> 01:01:02.006
two.

851
01:01:02.007 --> 01:01:03.007
one.

852
01:01:31.299 --> 01:01:32.716
Failed. huh?

853
01:01:32.717 --> 01:01:35.007
How will you explain that to the world?

854
01:01:35.008 --> 01:01:37.216
Another seven months wasted.

855
01:01:37.217 --> 01:01:38.424
It failed. right?

856
01:01:38.425 --> 01:01:40.300
What will you tell the world now?

857
01:02:00.342 --> 01:02:01.342
[No signal]

858
01:02:04.676 --> 01:02:08.176
Earth produced an angular displacement
of 2 pico arc seconds.

859
01:02:19.634 --> 01:02:20.551
We did it!

860
01:02:20.552 --> 01:02:21.801
It's working.

861
01:02:27.843 --> 01:02:29.343
Ignition is successful.

862
01:02:29.344 --> 01:02:31.844
We finally found a
direction for the future!

863
01:02:37.593 --> 01:02:40.843
The Moving Mountain
Project has been verified!

864
01:02:44.361 --> 01:02:46.288
I went to get your red envelope.

865
01:02:47.510 --> 01:02:48.884
- Please take a seat.
- Here?

866
01:02:48.885 --> 01:02:51.468
- Is this appropriate?
- Yes. it is.

867
01:02:51.469 --> 01:02:54.259
- Here. have a cigarette.
- I don't smoke.

868
01:02:54.260 --> 01:02:55.510
I'm the groom's dad.

869
01:02:57.927 --> 01:03:00.759
Your son's surname is Liu.
Why is your surname Zhang?

870
01:03:00.760 --> 01:03:05.384
Two successful engine ignition tests proved
550C's great potential in engine construction.

871
01:03:05.385 --> 01:03:09.634
Under 550C's coordination. the underground
cities' construction time is shortened by 75%.

872
01:03:09.635 --> 01:03:12.176
greatly reducing the Moving
Mountain Project's cost.

873
01:03:12.177 --> 01:03:15.176
Canada's geological
exploration is completed.

874
01:03:15.177 --> 01:03:18.121
Construction of North American Engines
will officially begin.

875
01:03:18.122 --> 01:03:19.675
The quantum computer 550 series

876
01:03:19.676 --> 01:03:23.218
is developing a higher computing power
engine-specific network based on 550C.

877
01:03:23.219 --> 01:03:26.067
According to a new round of surveys.
for the first time.

878
01:03:26.068 --> 01:03:30.010
public support for Moving Mountain
has overtaken that of Digital Life.

879
01:03:30.011 --> 01:03:32.760
The last batch of Space Elevator attackers
are now on public trial.

880
01:03:32.761 --> 01:03:35.859
This marks the complete obsolescence
of the Digital Life Project.

881
01:03:37.094 --> 01:03:38.594
You brats.

882
01:03:38.595 --> 01:03:43.136
I'll show you later what a
natural-born astronaut is.

883
01:03:45.094 --> 01:03:46.969
As the Space Elevator is being rebuilt.

884
01:03:46.970 --> 01:03:49.719
the UEG launched the
Navigator Project construction

885
01:03:49.720 --> 01:03:51.427
to provide early warning
for the Moving Mountain Project.

886
01:03:51.428 --> 01:03:55.511
Europe begins to cede rights for
more 550Cs to be used for construction.

887
01:03:59.386 --> 01:04:02.844
Sooner or later. we'll be
replaced by these things.

888
01:04:02.845 --> 01:04:06.470
Full automation has replaced
a great number of industrial workers.

889
01:04:06.471 --> 01:04:08.220
In the past 14 years.

890
01:04:08.221 --> 01:04:12.345
through self decision-making
and automated construction.

891
01:04:12.346 --> 01:04:17.178
the 550 series helped us
complete 5.321 engines.

892
01:04:17.179 --> 01:04:20.720
The Underground City Quota Lottery Plan was
passed at the UEG general assembly today.

893
01:04:20.721 --> 01:04:24.261
China's delegates strongly
protested its fairness.

894
01:04:24.262 --> 01:04:27.761
This lottery plan seriously contradicts the
Moving Mountain Project's original intention.

895
01:04:27.762 --> 01:04:31.011
Only half of the global population has
the chance to enter the underground cities.

896
01:04:31.012 --> 01:04:32.762
As Earth's rotation gradually stops.

897
01:04:32.763 --> 01:04:35.805
we'll switch from a 24-hour time system
to a 60-hour one.

898
01:04:36.887 --> 01:04:40.990
The surge in solar radiation has led to an
explosive growth of cancer around the world.

899
01:04:40.991 --> 01:04:42.720
We've been through hardships.

900
01:04:42.721 --> 01:04:47.179
We've given resources. time. and even life.

901
01:04:47.180 --> 01:04:50.971
At the same time.
we also gained mutual aid and solidarity.

902
01:04:50.972 --> 01:04:54.512
Get lost. Don't let robots take our jobs.

903
01:04:54.513 --> 01:04:56.757
Look at their suits.
Sooner or later. they'll be replaced.

904
01:04:56.758 --> 01:04:59.262
Welcome to Sulawesi
Automated Construction Site.

905
01:04:59.263 --> 01:05:03.762
550W. an upgraded version
of the quantum computer 550C.

906
01:05:03.763 --> 01:05:05.846
enters offline testing phase.

907
01:05:05.847 --> 01:05:10.972
It's estimated to build the control network for
Earth Engines globally in the next ten years.

908
01:05:14.888 --> 01:05:16.512
It's fine.

909
01:05:16.513 --> 01:05:18.471
I can just apply to be a navigator. [You are
qualified to enter the underground city]

910
01:05:18.472 --> 01:05:20.304
Our son has a slot too.

911
01:05:20.305 --> 01:05:26.055
We're all invited to safeguard
the unity of mankind together.

912
01:05:26.056 --> 01:05:27.139
On behalf of China.

913
01:05:28.098 --> 01:05:30.888
please allow me to solemnly announce

914
01:05:30.889 --> 01:05:34.223
the official renaming of
the Moving Mountain Project

915
01:05:34.224 --> 01:05:36.170
to the Wandering Earth Project.

916
01:05:50.639 --> 01:05:56.013
In the past 28 years. there have been
9.1 billion cyberattacks against us.

917
01:05:56.014 --> 01:05:59.847
7.9 billion of these were
made in the year 2044 alone.

918
01:05:59.848 --> 01:06:03.180
In January. there were
30 million cyberattacks.

919
01:06:03.181 --> 01:06:05.138
Over the past several months.

920
01:06:05.139 --> 01:06:10.098
we have seen the infrastructure of
New York City and UEG Headquarters

921
01:06:10.099 --> 01:06:11.514
damaged beyond repair.

922
01:06:11.515 --> 01:06:15.056
And in March this year. there
were 4.4 billion attacks.

923
01:06:15.057 --> 01:06:17.348
The Space Elevator was also attacked

924
01:06:17.349 --> 01:06:20.306
which resulted in the fall
of the Ark Space Station.

925
01:06:20.307 --> 01:06:22.139
On the lunar base. the life support

926
01:06:22.140 --> 01:06:24.639
- and early warning systems were disabled.
- However.

927
01:06:24.640 --> 01:06:26.431
in the last decade.

928
01:06:26.432 --> 01:06:29.807
over 10.000 attackers and organizers
have been arrested.

929
01:06:30.640 --> 01:06:34.224
We have put a stop to
the Digital Life Project.

930
01:06:35.224 --> 01:06:36.723
Speaking of which.

931
01:06:36.724 --> 01:06:41.514
digital technology has greatly enhanced
our construction efficiency.

932
01:06:41.515 --> 01:06:45.140
The risks are nothing
compared to the benefits.

933
01:06:51.725 --> 01:06:56.224
This photo was received
by Institute 710 in 1987.

934
01:06:56.225 --> 01:06:59.349
It says. "2044".

935
01:06:59.350 --> 01:07:00.742
The source is unknown.

936
01:07:03.350 --> 01:07:07.974
The second one was received by our Ultrafast
Optical Femtosecond Lab last week.

937
01:07:07.975 --> 01:07:11.140
It says. "205807".

938
01:07:11.141 --> 01:07:12.682
The source is unknown.

939
01:07:12.683 --> 01:07:17.640
This information concerns
thousands of laboratories worldwide.

940
01:07:17.641 --> 01:07:21.890
I believe all countries' intelligence
agencies received messages like this.

941
01:07:21.891 --> 01:07:25.183
We speculate that this is
a kind of warning message.

942
01:07:25.933 --> 01:07:29.392
We all know what we experienced in 2044.

943
01:07:30.601 --> 01:07:32.809
We hope all parties will take it seriously.

944
01:07:45.059 --> 01:07:47.766
Today is June 22nd. 2058.

945
01:07:47.767 --> 01:07:51.017
What was just unveiled behind me
is the Moon Departure Monument.

946
01:07:52.351 --> 01:07:53.351
Xiaoxi.

947
01:07:58.101 --> 01:07:59.101
Have a seat.

948
01:08:00.976 --> 01:08:05.683
Any reply on the Moon's backup plan?

949
01:08:05.684 --> 01:08:09.809
Some countries raised objections.
They didn't sign it.

950
01:08:09.810 --> 01:08:12.977
The main disagreement
is the strategic nuclear weapons' donation.

951
01:08:15.518 --> 01:08:18.435
I'm afraid it will end
up like 14 years ago.

952
01:08:20.060 --> 01:08:24.184
Take strict precautions
and make a backup plan.

953
01:08:24.185 --> 01:08:28.815
[7 days to the lunar crisis]

954
01:08:31.768 --> 01:08:36.101
[Paris]

955
01:08:36.102 --> 01:08:40.517
[UEG Spaceflight Control Center]

956
01:08:40.518 --> 01:08:43.934
In my estimation. the
key is the bean itself.

957
01:08:43.935 --> 01:08:50.602
Now there are many exceptional beans that come
from places like Sumatra and even Kathmandu.

958
01:08:50.603 --> 01:08:53.018
When the Moon is too far to be seen.

959
01:08:53.019 --> 01:08:55.419
I wonder if we'll still have
the Mid-Autumn Festival holiday.

960
01:08:57.018 --> 01:08:59.060
It's fine as long as we can eat mooncakes.

961
01:08:59.061 --> 01:09:00.610
Preferably with meat filling.

962
01:09:01.853 --> 01:09:04.368
Buddy. are you sure you're
talking about mooncakes?

963
01:09:05.686 --> 01:09:07.048
You're from the North.

964
01:09:14.019 --> 01:09:16.746
The people today didn't see
the Moon in ancient times.

965
01:09:16.747 --> 01:09:20.018
but the Moon once shone on ancient people.

966
01:09:20.019 --> 01:09:26.352
The Moon will always stay in people's
memories as our longing for our hometown.

967
01:09:26.353 --> 01:09:28.353
As the Lunar Exile Project initiates.
[Beijing]

968
01:09:28.354 --> 01:09:29.769
let us once again

969
01:09:29.770 --> 01:09:32.228
- offer our blessings to the Moon.
- Ready.

970
01:09:32.229 --> 01:09:34.561
A big watermelon

971
01:09:34.562 --> 01:09:36.603
sliced in half.

972
01:09:36.604 --> 01:09:38.228
Half for you.

973
01:09:38.229 --> 01:09:39.686
half for your mom.

974
01:09:39.687 --> 01:09:41.186
One half.

975
01:09:41.187 --> 01:09:42.561
Come here.

976
01:09:42.562 --> 01:09:43.562
Come here.

977
01:09:44.354 --> 01:09:45.354
One. two.

978
01:09:47.770 --> 01:09:48.812
Go. Blow on it.

979
01:09:51.270 --> 01:09:54.853
These are for you two.

980
01:09:54.854 --> 01:09:56.603
I want to take photos with my phone.

981
01:09:56.604 --> 01:09:58.270
I want to edit them with my phone.

982
01:09:58.271 --> 01:10:01.021
I'm going to edit photos.

983
01:10:01.937 --> 01:10:03.603
Mom. I want to edit photos too.

984
01:10:03.604 --> 01:10:04.853
Wait. let me do it first.

985
01:10:04.854 --> 01:10:06.644
Mom. let me do it too.

986
01:10:06.645 --> 01:10:08.895
Be patient. Let me finish first.

987
01:10:08.896 --> 01:10:10.312
- Let me edit them too.
- Wait.

988
01:10:10.313 --> 01:10:11.855
Wait until I'm done. okay?

989
01:10:18.896 --> 01:10:20.562
It's okay.

990
01:10:20.563 --> 01:10:22.814
I won't edit them anymore. Don't be scared.

991
01:10:23.563 --> 01:10:24.894
Liu Qi. don't be scared.

992
01:10:25.563 --> 01:10:26.730
It's okay.

993
01:10:28.021 --> 01:10:29.105
It's fine.

994
01:10:29.855 --> 01:10:30.855
Don't cry.

995
01:10:31.938 --> 01:10:33.021
Don't cry.

996
01:10:38.605 --> 01:10:40.770
I know what you're thinking.

997
01:10:40.771 --> 01:10:44.437
Do you know how many people in the world can't
get a slot to enter the underground cities?

998
01:10:44.438 --> 01:10:47.062
Do you know how many would want your slot?

999
01:10:47.063 --> 01:10:49.664
You should be happy that
Yaya is not living in this kind of world.

1000
01:10:50.771 --> 01:10:52.646
Even if the Internet has
been shut down globally.

1001
01:10:52.647 --> 01:10:55.231
550W retains all local
area network interfaces.

1002
01:10:55.980 --> 01:10:58.188
If you connect Tu Yaya to 550W.

1003
01:10:58.189 --> 01:11:00.188
you'll be disqualified immediately.

1004
01:11:00.189 --> 01:11:01.759
Then you'll be imprisoned.

1005
01:11:10.814 --> 01:11:12.189
What about my daughter?

1006
01:11:14.314 --> 01:11:16.314
I haven't seen her in 14 years.

1007
01:11:23.439 --> 01:11:25.480
Yaya is already dead.

1008
01:11:25.481 --> 01:11:26.522
That's reality.

1009
01:11:27.646 --> 01:11:30.273
No. Yaya isn't dead.

1010
01:11:32.898 --> 01:11:35.357
I don't agree with your
view on digital life.

1011
01:11:37.357 --> 01:11:39.560
I've waited 14 years.

1012
01:11:39.561 --> 01:11:40.936
I'm old.

1013
01:11:42.315 --> 01:11:44.939
Even if I go to the underground city.

1014
01:11:44.940 --> 01:11:47.231
how many more 14 years do I have?

1015
01:11:47.232 --> 01:11:48.772
Dad.

1016
01:11:48.773 --> 01:11:51.856
I want to have ice cream first
in the amusement park.

1017
01:11:51.857 --> 01:11:54.231
Do you want strawberry or milk flavor?

1018
01:11:54.232 --> 01:11:56.689
I want the biggest one.
the one that's bigger than me.

1019
01:11:56.690 --> 01:11:58.231
Have one of each.

1020
01:11:58.232 --> 01:12:00.981
Your mom is the one
who always eats them in the end.

1021
01:12:00.982 --> 01:12:03.022
All my teeth will fall out.

1022
01:12:03.023 --> 01:12:04.232
Will that be okay?

1023
01:12:05.523 --> 01:12:08.315
If Yaya can successfully connect to 550W.

1024
01:12:09.214 --> 01:12:11.792
it will be a milestone
in digital life creation.

1025
01:12:13.483 --> 01:12:14.524
There.

1026
01:12:15.316 --> 01:12:17.649
she'll have a complete life.

1027
01:12:19.108 --> 01:12:22.899
And your name will be written in history.

1028
01:12:25.524 --> 01:12:29.067
If you initiate Yaya. you'll die.
If you don't do anything. you'll live.

1029
01:12:30.024 --> 01:12:31.245
It's your choice.

1030
01:12:38.482 --> 01:12:40.773
Navigator interviewees.
pay attention to the number called.

1031
01:12:40.774 --> 01:12:42.774
Don't linger in the hallway.
[Beijing Space Center]

1032
01:12:44.774 --> 01:12:46.899
Hello. Lieutenant Colonel Liu Peiqiang.

1033
01:12:48.399 --> 01:12:51.691
I'm the Manned Orbital Space
Station Control System.

1034
01:12:51.692 --> 01:12:54.274
550W's offline version.

1035
01:12:54.275 --> 01:12:57.308
Quantum size 8.192.
[Intelligent Quantum Computer 550W]

1036
01:12:57.309 --> 01:13:00.649
The most powerful computing hardware
in the history of mankind as of now.

1037
01:13:00.650 --> 01:13:02.108
According to prior evaluation.

1038
01:13:02.109 --> 01:13:06.816
all of your flight records
and exam grades are impeccable.

1039
01:13:06.817 --> 01:13:11.483
I think you have a great chance to be
stationed at the Navigator Space Station.

1040
01:13:11.484 --> 01:13:12.816
Thank you.

1041
01:13:12.817 --> 01:13:14.698
I've longed for the
space since I was a kid.

1042
01:13:14.699 --> 01:13:17.149
I hope to roam it on behalf of humanity.

1043
01:13:17.150 --> 01:13:19.024
To better understand each other.

1044
01:13:19.025 --> 01:13:22.816
I'm very interested to know
what your first impression of me is.

1045
01:13:22.817 --> 01:13:23.899
Five.

1046
01:13:23.900 --> 01:13:24.900
Four.

1047
01:13:24.901 --> 01:13:27.317
- Three.
- Why do you only have one eye?

1048
01:13:28.234 --> 01:13:30.692
I have two versions of the answer.

1049
01:13:30.693 --> 01:13:34.275
The one with a great sense of humor
is it's easier to focus with one eye.

1050
01:13:34.276 --> 01:13:36.525
Then I can look at you better.

1051
01:13:36.526 --> 01:13:37.651
Hahaha.

1052
01:13:39.526 --> 01:13:40.860
This sense of humor...

1053
01:13:43.026 --> 01:13:44.216
is just right.

1054
01:13:46.235 --> 01:13:49.859
The official answer is
this is my ToF radar unit.

1055
01:13:49.860 --> 01:13:52.192
At the same time.
it can mobilize all networked devices

1056
01:13:52.193 --> 01:13:55.484
to carry out multi-angle
data information collection

1057
01:13:55.485 --> 01:13:57.567
such as biological indicators
and related data on the target.

1058
01:13:57.568 --> 01:14:00.525
For example. you're married with a son.

1059
01:14:00.526 --> 01:14:03.984
Three years ago. your wife
got type II radiation sickness.

1060
01:14:03.985 --> 01:14:06.317
She recently got Lynch syndrome.

1061
01:14:06.318 --> 01:14:09.694
Under these circumstances.
your best option should be

1062
01:14:09.695 --> 01:14:12.818
to give up the selection
and take care of your family.

1063
01:14:12.819 --> 01:14:13.819
Five.

1064
01:14:13.820 --> 01:14:15.151
Four.

1065
01:14:15.152 --> 01:14:16.235
Three.

1066
01:14:16.236 --> 01:14:17.194
Two.

1067
01:14:17.195 --> 01:14:18.235
One.

1068
01:14:18.236 --> 01:14:21.735
Since ancient times. loyalty and
filial piety can't both be satisfied.

1069
01:14:21.736 --> 01:14:22.985
Please pay attention.

1070
01:14:22.986 --> 01:14:24.735
In your next answers.

1071
01:14:24.736 --> 01:14:28.943
metaphors. rhetorical questions.
and allusions aren't allowed.

1072
01:14:28.944 --> 01:14:32.402
These types of communication can cause
serious Space Station incidents.

1073
01:14:33.152 --> 01:14:34.069
Five.

1074
01:14:34.070 --> 01:14:35.652
Four.

1075
01:14:35.653 --> 01:14:38.772
- Three.
- I feel bad about leaving my family behind.

1076
01:14:40.527 --> 01:14:42.985
But this is something I must do.

1077
01:14:42.986 --> 01:14:45.151
By "something you must do".

1078
01:14:45.152 --> 01:14:48.027
do you mean you're forced to do this job?

1079
01:14:48.902 --> 01:14:49.944
Five.

1080
01:14:49.945 --> 01:14:51.277
Four.

1081
01:14:51.278 --> 01:14:52.195
Three.

1082
01:14:52.195 --> 01:14:53.195
Two.

1083
01:14:54.028 --> 01:14:55.843
You all obviously know everything.

1084
01:14:57.362 --> 01:14:58.890
Why must you still do this?

1085
01:15:01.445 --> 01:15:02.902
Second warning.

1086
01:15:02.903 --> 01:15:06.695
Metaphors. rhetorical questions.
and allusions aren't allowed.

1087
01:15:08.028 --> 01:15:09.187
I got a slot.

1088
01:15:11.403 --> 01:15:12.862
But my wife and son didn't.

1089
01:15:14.987 --> 01:15:17.101
As long as I get selected
for the Space Station.

1090
01:15:18.153 --> 01:15:20.112
my son can become a preferred person.

1091
01:15:21.695 --> 01:15:24.569
My wife can also enter
the underground city with my son

1092
01:15:24.570 --> 01:15:26.695
as the guardian of a minor.

1093
01:15:28.195 --> 01:15:30.404
I just want my family to live on.

1094
01:15:36.904 --> 01:15:37.904
Dad.

1095
01:15:40.696 --> 01:15:42.446
What about your other family member?

1096
01:15:43.404 --> 01:15:45.153
What do you mean?

1097
01:15:45.154 --> 01:15:46.528
Lieutenant Colonel Liu Peiqiang.

1098
01:15:46.529 --> 01:15:49.778
Your father-in-law. Mr. Han Zi'ang.
didn't get a slot too.

1099
01:15:49.779 --> 01:15:51.571
What about Mr. Han Zi'ang?

1100
01:15:52.821 --> 01:15:53.738
Five.

1101
01:15:53.738 --> 01:15:54.654
Four.

1102
01:15:54.655 --> 01:15:55.987
Three.

1103
01:15:55.988 --> 01:15:56.946
Two.

1104
01:15:56.946 --> 01:15:57.946
One.

1105
01:15:58.779 --> 01:16:00.154
Response time limit exceeded.

1106
01:16:02.071 --> 01:16:06.362
Your best option is to let
Mr. Han Zi'ang become the guardian

1107
01:16:06.363 --> 01:16:08.612
to take Liu Qi to the underground city.

1108
01:16:08.613 --> 01:16:13.740
Based on your wife's vital signs.
her life will end after 84.3 days.

1109
01:16:17.530 --> 01:16:19.155
Fuck you all! I...

1110
01:16:20.030 --> 01:16:21.989
You failed the stress response test.

1111
01:16:29.697 --> 01:16:30.697
I'm sorry.

1112
01:16:31.405 --> 01:16:32.447
I'm sorry.

1113
01:16:33.197 --> 01:16:34.197
I'm sorry.

1114
01:16:39.280 --> 01:16:40.280
Go to Number 19.

1115
01:16:44.489 --> 01:16:45.489
I'm sorry.

1116
01:16:50.697 --> 01:16:51.822
Sir.

1117
01:16:51.823 --> 01:16:52.990
Can I try again?

1118
01:16:57.615 --> 01:16:59.115
You didn't pass the exam.

1119
01:17:00.198 --> 01:17:01.115
Sir.

1120
01:17:01.116 --> 01:17:02.864
I was too nervous at the interview.

1121
01:17:02.865 --> 01:17:05.221
I'm not usually like that.
Please give me another chance.

1122
01:17:05.222 --> 01:17:08.489
This exam is very
important to everyone here.

1123
01:17:08.490 --> 01:17:10.489
Don't affect them. okay?

1124
01:17:10.490 --> 01:17:12.572
I really need this chance.

1125
01:17:12.573 --> 01:17:13.739
I really need it.

1126
01:17:13.740 --> 01:17:15.365
Everyone only gets one chance here.

1127
01:17:24.198 --> 01:17:28.073
[21 hours to the lunar crisis]

1128
01:17:29.697 --> 01:17:31.823
Do you have a mistress on the Moon or what?

1129
01:17:31.824 --> 01:17:33.281
You're so eager to see the Moon go.

1130
01:17:33.282 --> 01:17:35.531
He does. She was his university classmate.

1131
01:17:35.532 --> 01:17:36.906
Nonsense. it's not her.

1132
01:17:36.907 --> 01:17:38.324
Who is it then?

1133
01:17:38.991 --> 01:17:42.323
Listen. The Moon is just
pushed yearly by 10.000...

1134
01:17:42.324 --> 01:17:43.365
10.000. right?

1135
01:17:43.366 --> 01:17:46.156
10.000 km. It will be a long wait.

1136
01:17:46.157 --> 01:17:47.365
Listen up. everyone.

1137
01:17:47.366 --> 01:17:49.365
Don't panic. Maintain order.

1138
01:17:49.366 --> 01:17:50.823
The weather is cold.

1139
01:17:50.824 --> 01:17:54.031
Line up properly. There's
enough for everyone.

1140
01:17:54.032 --> 01:17:55.906
Hold on to your cards. All right?

1141
01:17:55.907 --> 01:17:57.656
- Thank you for your cooperation.
- Maintain order.

1142
01:17:57.657 --> 01:17:59.751
I guarantee. everyone
can get their supplies.

1143
01:17:59.752 --> 01:18:02.489
- It's cold. my son can't take it anymore.
- Next.

1144
01:18:02.490 --> 01:18:04.406
My son has a fever. Can we switch places?

1145
01:18:04.407 --> 01:18:06.990
Come here. I'll switch with you.

1146
01:18:06.991 --> 01:18:09.238
- Those at the back. line up properly.
- Your turn.

1147
01:18:10.574 --> 01:18:12.824
- Comrade. What are you doing?
- Take it.

1148
01:18:12.825 --> 01:18:14.116
Please line up properly.

1149
01:18:14.117 --> 01:18:15.497
Everyone is lining up.

1150
01:18:18.325 --> 01:18:20.765
- Meritorious service in 2044?
- Don't let people cut in line.

1151
01:18:21.908 --> 01:18:24.268
- My wife's undergoing chemotherapy.
- Here are your fruits.

1152
01:18:26.782 --> 01:18:28.199
- Next.
- Thank you.

1153
01:18:28.200 --> 01:18:30.074
- Next.
- Please.

1154
01:18:30.075 --> 01:18:31.341
- Take it.
- This is yours.

1155
01:18:37.908 --> 01:18:39.658
- Next.
- Maintain order.

1156
01:18:49.075 --> 01:18:50.075
Liu Qi.

1157
01:18:58.068 --> 01:18:59.276
Mom. you eat first.

1158
01:19:13.048 --> 01:19:14.409
Focus on your interview.

1159
01:19:16.076 --> 01:19:17.576
You'll make it.

1160
01:19:18.993 --> 01:19:19.993
Honey.

1161
01:19:23.826 --> 01:19:25.243
Today. I just...

1162
01:19:27.201 --> 01:19:28.201
really missed you.

1163
01:19:31.243 --> 01:19:32.244
A lot.

1164
01:19:35.619 --> 01:19:36.660
Very much.

1165
01:19:46.202 --> 01:19:47.244
It's okay.

1166
01:19:50.577 --> 01:19:51.702
I'm here.

1167
01:19:57.994 --> 01:19:59.202
I'm always here.

1168
01:20:15.203 --> 01:20:16.203
Peiqiang.

1169
01:20:19.870 --> 01:20:21.661
I want to go back home.

1170
01:20:24.745 --> 01:20:25.886
Go back...

1171
01:20:28.244 --> 01:20:29.952
to Shanghai?

1172
01:20:29.953 --> 01:20:31.828
I know that place is already...

1173
01:20:37.786 --> 01:20:39.120
I'm just saying it.

1174
01:20:40.286 --> 01:20:41.536
I'm just saying it.

1175
01:21:25.614 --> 01:21:30.473
[44 minutes to the lunar crisis]

1176
01:23:04.040 --> 01:23:05.040
Dad.

1177
01:23:07.749 --> 01:23:10.040
Dad. how do I solve this?

1178
01:23:11.374 --> 01:23:12.831
Where are you. Dad?

1179
01:23:12.832 --> 01:23:14.873
It's like there are
many of you in the back.

1180
01:23:14.874 --> 01:23:16.540
Is there a mirror behind you?

1181
01:23:20.006 --> 01:23:22.131
Dad. why are you crying?

1182
01:23:23.957 --> 01:23:25.748
Dad. what's wrong?

1183
01:23:25.749 --> 01:23:27.457
Why did you age so much?

1184
01:23:29.415 --> 01:23:32.929
Don't cry. Dad. Did I do something wrong?

1185
01:23:34.541 --> 01:23:36.083
I miss you so much.

1186
01:23:38.166 --> 01:23:39.208
A lot.

1187
01:23:40.458 --> 01:23:42.249
Very much.

1188
01:23:42.250 --> 01:23:45.957
Aren't we going to the amusement park?

1189
01:23:45.958 --> 01:23:47.083
Where's Mom?

1190
01:23:50.125 --> 01:23:52.415
It's right ahead. The third room.

1191
01:23:52.416 --> 01:23:54.290
Dad. where is this place?

1192
01:23:54.291 --> 01:23:55.916
I want to go out.

1193
01:23:57.541 --> 01:23:58.459
One moment.

1194
01:23:58.460 --> 01:24:00.709
Dad. I want to go out.

1195
01:24:01.790 --> 01:24:04.790
Dad. where is this place? I want to go out.

1196
01:24:04.791 --> 01:24:06.457
Dad. where am I?

1197
01:24:06.458 --> 01:24:08.707
- I want to go out!
- Don't be scared.

1198
01:24:08.708 --> 01:24:09.875
I'm here.

1199
01:24:11.000 --> 01:24:12.790
Tu Hengyu. open the door.

1200
01:24:12.791 --> 01:24:13.791
Open up.

1201
01:24:17.084 --> 01:24:21.000
Dad. I want a hug.

1202
01:24:21.001 --> 01:24:22.353
Here you go.

1203
01:24:23.165 --> 01:24:24.625
Wait for me.

1204
01:24:24.626 --> 01:24:26.666
Tu Hengyu. what are you doing?

1205
01:24:26.667 --> 01:24:27.667
Stop it.

1206
01:24:28.959 --> 01:24:30.376
[Upload data to 550W?]

1207
01:24:36.416 --> 01:24:37.875
Tu Hengyu.

1208
01:24:37.876 --> 01:24:38.876
Come out.

1209
01:24:42.334 --> 01:24:44.459
Yaya just needs 87 seconds now...

1210
01:24:45.584 --> 01:24:47.458
to form self-awareness.

1211
01:24:47.459 --> 01:24:49.001
This is just the result
of iterative evolution.

1212
01:24:49.002 --> 01:24:50.043
No.

1213
01:24:50.709 --> 01:24:53.376
This is your narrow
understanding of digital life.

1214
01:24:54.334 --> 01:24:58.542
This actually proves that Yaya is alive.

1215
01:24:58.543 --> 01:25:00.376
She's gone.

1216
01:25:00.377 --> 01:25:02.771
- You're committing a crime.
- Dad. how do I solve this?

1217
01:25:02.772 --> 01:25:04.688
Yaya can only live for two minutes.

1218
01:25:07.334 --> 01:25:09.751
I want to give her a complete life.

1219
01:25:09.752 --> 01:25:12.966
You got a slot. You have
a long future ahead.

1220
01:25:12.967 --> 01:25:16.127
- Live in reality.
- Dad. who are you talking to?

1221
01:25:17.252 --> 01:25:19.224
Yaya is already dead.

1222
01:25:19.225 --> 01:25:20.225
She's not!

1223
01:25:21.501 --> 01:25:23.376
She's not!

1224
01:25:23.377 --> 01:25:24.917
This is reality.

1225
01:25:24.918 --> 01:25:26.542
No.

1226
01:25:26.543 --> 01:25:27.543
No.

1227
01:25:28.377 --> 01:25:30.793
You're not qualified to
define what reality is.

1228
01:25:31.877 --> 01:25:32.877
Hurry.

1229
01:25:32.878 --> 01:25:34.073
Mr. Ma. step back a bit.

1230
01:25:34.752 --> 01:25:37.294
Yaya will surely live on.
[14 seconds to the lunar crisis]

1231
01:26:15.920 --> 01:26:19.628
Warning. Lunar 1 Satellite
Engine malfunction.

1232
01:26:19.629 --> 01:26:22.669
Warning. Lunar 1 Satellite
Engine malfunction.

1233
01:26:22.670 --> 01:26:23.670
Technician!

1234
01:26:24.337 --> 01:26:25.337
Technician!

1235
01:26:26.420 --> 01:26:28.129
Get all the technicians here!

1236
01:26:29.337 --> 01:26:32.169
Do everything you can
to shut down Engine 1.

1237
01:26:32.170 --> 01:26:33.715
At this rate. it will explode.

1238
01:27:16.296 --> 01:27:17.255
Dad!

1239
01:27:17.256 --> 01:27:18.754
Dad!

1240
01:27:18.755 --> 01:27:19.837
Dad!

1241
01:27:19.838 --> 01:27:21.545
Don't hurt my dad.

1242
01:27:21.546 --> 01:27:23.545
My dad is a good person.

1243
01:27:23.546 --> 01:27:24.677
Take him away.

1244
01:27:25.588 --> 01:27:27.154
The suspect is under control.

1245
01:27:28.005 --> 01:27:30.255
Dad. where are you going?

1246
01:27:34.963 --> 01:27:37.590
Mr. Ma. I want my dad.

1247
01:27:38.297 --> 01:27:39.506
Dad.

1248
01:28:04.589 --> 01:28:07.546
Mr. Liu. the application for jet use
has been specially approved by the boss.

1249
01:28:07.547 --> 01:28:08.974
And he wants to send his
regards to your wife.

1250
01:28:08.975 --> 01:28:11.255
Thank you. buddy. I'll buy
you drinks when I get back.

1251
01:28:11.256 --> 01:28:12.338
Hello. Mrs. Liu!

1252
01:28:12.339 --> 01:28:14.046
- Hi. Mrs. Liu.
- Hi. Mrs. Liu.

1253
01:28:14.047 --> 01:28:15.838
- It must be hard on you. Mrs. Liu.
- Hi. Mrs. Liu.

1254
01:28:15.839 --> 01:28:18.798
- It must be hard on you. Mrs. Liu.
- Thank you. guys!

1255
01:28:19.798 --> 01:28:20.882
Peiqiang.

1256
01:28:21.632 --> 01:28:25.339
You haven't flown in years.
Can you still do it?

1257
01:28:25.340 --> 01:28:26.714
Keep it steady.

1258
01:28:26.715 --> 01:28:29.131
Liu Peiqiang!

1259
01:28:29.132 --> 01:28:31.839
Are you riding a bike?

1260
01:28:31.840 --> 01:28:34.090
Go faster!

1261
01:29:14.430 --> 01:29:16.090
Peiqiang.
[Shanghai]

1262
01:29:16.091 --> 01:29:17.091
This way.

1263
01:29:23.633 --> 01:29:24.965
Are you okay?

1264
01:29:24.966 --> 01:29:25.966
Yes.

1265
01:29:30.674 --> 01:29:34.632
Whenever I couldn't
sleep when I was little.

1266
01:29:34.633 --> 01:29:36.758
I would sit here and look at the Moon.

1267
01:29:37.925 --> 01:29:38.986
I think...

1268
01:29:41.134 --> 01:29:42.556
my chances aren't good.

1269
01:29:47.967 --> 01:29:49.384
I already have a plan.

1270
01:29:51.393 --> 01:29:52.893
If you don't get selected.

1271
01:29:53.884 --> 01:29:55.384
go down...

1272
01:29:56.592 --> 01:29:57.967
and live well.

1273
01:29:59.884 --> 01:30:01.134
If you get selected.

1274
01:30:02.592 --> 01:30:04.925
our dad will bring our son
to the underground city.

1275
01:30:07.259 --> 01:30:09.175
I won't occupy the slot.

1276
01:30:14.509 --> 01:30:15.509
Also.

1277
01:30:17.593 --> 01:30:18.926
when my time comes.

1278
01:30:20.635 --> 01:30:23.218
don't stick a bunch of tubes on me.

1279
01:30:33.171 --> 01:30:34.171
Peiqiang.

1280
01:30:43.593 --> 01:30:44.593
Don't be scared.

1281
01:30:49.593 --> 01:30:50.885
I'm here.

1282
01:30:54.635 --> 01:30:55.926
I'm always here.

1283
01:31:05.594 --> 01:31:09.135
Sir. the lunar engine's operating system
has been overwritten.

1284
01:31:09.136 --> 01:31:12.801
The code is similar to the
2044 Space Elevator attack.

1285
01:31:12.802 --> 01:31:16.360
We tried to overwrite the operating system
with 550W. but access was denied.

1286
01:31:16.361 --> 01:31:18.635
Who did it? Who exactly did it?

1287
01:31:18.636 --> 01:31:20.480
Do we have any staff on the Moon?

1288
01:31:21.135 --> 01:31:22.635
Yes. a robot.

1289
01:31:22.636 --> 01:31:26.802
Warning. Lunar 2 Satellite Engine's
exceeding normal power level.

1290
01:31:47.927 --> 01:31:49.427
Stand back!

1291
01:31:49.428 --> 01:31:51.094
I'll say it again.

1292
01:31:51.095 --> 01:31:52.636
Your acts of protest

1293
01:31:52.637 --> 01:31:57.636
have seriously interfered with
the operation of New York Earth Engine 1.

1294
01:31:57.637 --> 01:31:59.761
According to Article 551.

1295
01:31:59.762 --> 01:32:01.689
paragraph 5 of the Wandering Earth Act...

1296
01:32:01.690 --> 01:32:03.094
Xiaoxi.

1297
01:32:03.095 --> 01:32:04.928
Is that a seagull?

1298
01:32:08.928 --> 01:32:11.178
I haven't really seen one. Mr. Zhou.

1299
01:32:13.637 --> 01:32:15.511
Earth stopped rotating for so long.

1300
01:32:15.512 --> 01:32:17.178
How did it survive?

1301
01:32:43.178 --> 01:32:44.970
I'm already in the building.

1302
01:32:44.971 --> 01:32:46.209
You got it too?

1303
01:32:50.346 --> 01:32:52.302
I heard something is
happening with the Moon.

1304
01:33:26.097 --> 01:33:27.597
Run!

1305
01:33:29.139 --> 01:33:30.139
Watch out!

1306
01:33:44.431 --> 01:33:45.931
Urgent call of duty?

1307
01:33:47.931 --> 01:33:50.349
Dad. look. The Moon is suddenly shining.

1308
01:34:08.640 --> 01:34:10.431
This is too hard.

1309
01:34:19.098 --> 01:34:23.431
Extreme tidal could be incoming
if it changes the lunar orbit.

1310
01:34:23.432 --> 01:34:27.265
Residents in coastal regions
shall seek cover on high ground.

1311
01:34:27.266 --> 01:34:28.266
Yes.

1312
01:34:34.766 --> 01:34:36.474
Father. look.

1313
01:34:37.724 --> 01:34:39.474
This is bad.

1314
01:34:40.432 --> 01:34:42.181
Dear.

1315
01:34:42.182 --> 01:34:43.890
Look at this.

1316
01:34:43.891 --> 01:34:45.056
What's going on?

1317
01:34:45.057 --> 01:34:48.141
- Did you hear what happened?
- Yes. I did.

1318
01:34:53.349 --> 01:34:56.057
I told you.

1319
01:34:57.431 --> 01:34:59.181
Dude. we're so dead!

1320
01:34:59.182 --> 01:35:01.268
- The Moon is falling!
- We're so dead!

1321
01:35:02.725 --> 01:35:05.599
Now. the Lunar 2 Satellite Engine is gone.

1322
01:35:05.600 --> 01:35:07.724
Lunar 3 must remain functional.

1323
01:35:07.725 --> 01:35:09.475
CSST has sent back a video.

1324
01:35:10.558 --> 01:35:11.558
Broadcast it.

1325
01:35:13.892 --> 01:35:16.266
It wouldn't be so bright
if it was a shutdown.

1326
01:35:16.267 --> 01:35:19.559
But based on the current data.
we can only do such judgement.

1327
01:35:22.975 --> 01:35:25.224
Lunar 3 has exploded too.

1328
01:35:25.225 --> 01:35:27.849
The Moon is off its orbit
and crashing into us.

1329
01:35:27.850 --> 01:35:30.141
We should have 221 hours left.

1330
01:35:30.142 --> 01:35:32.641
Less than four days.
What are we waiting for?

1331
01:35:32.642 --> 01:35:34.599
Initiate the Earth Engines now.

1332
01:35:34.600 --> 01:35:37.682
Earth is still here. It will be destroyed
if we initiate them.

1333
01:35:37.683 --> 01:35:40.100
Besides. our Earth Engine construction
is only two-thirds completed.

1334
01:35:40.101 --> 01:35:42.727
So we'll just wait to die?

1335
01:35:48.135 --> 01:35:51.010
Our country is opening
up all underground cities

1336
01:35:51.011 --> 01:35:53.719
to maximize the safety of
people in our territory.

1337
01:35:55.726 --> 01:35:57.017
Young lady.

1338
01:35:57.018 --> 01:35:59.058
If we let them all in now.

1339
01:35:59.059 --> 01:36:03.308
they'll simply settle down
and never come back up.

1340
01:36:03.309 --> 01:36:07.267
Wait and see what happens
when the food runs out.

1341
01:36:07.268 --> 01:36:09.309
we will all starve to death.

1342
01:36:11.559 --> 01:36:15.185
We're informing you of our decision
to open up underground cities.

1343
01:36:16.268 --> 01:36:18.226
We're not asking for your advice.

1344
01:36:34.644 --> 01:36:38.311
[179 hours to the Moon disintegrates]

1345
01:36:38.312 --> 01:36:39.413
Salute.

1346
01:36:41.894 --> 01:36:43.174
There's no need for the lottery.

1347
01:36:45.060 --> 01:36:48.647
You can directly qualify
to live in the underground city.

1348
01:36:51.560 --> 01:36:52.644
After I leave.

1349
01:36:54.394 --> 01:36:56.435
you'll be Liu Qi's sole guardian.

1350
01:36:58.352 --> 01:37:00.366
This is also the only way...
[The Navigation ISS]

1351
01:37:01.310 --> 01:37:03.352
for you and Liu Qi to survive.

1352
01:37:03.353 --> 01:37:04.477
All right.

1353
01:37:04.478 --> 01:37:05.603
Stop talking.

1354
01:37:08.228 --> 01:37:09.228
I'm sorry.

1355
01:37:19.228 --> 01:37:20.644
Temporary crew members.

1356
01:37:20.645 --> 01:37:23.727
Welcome to the Navigation Platform ISS.

1357
01:37:23.728 --> 01:37:27.852
Please report to Docking Hall No. 4
at your earliest convenience.

1358
01:37:27.853 --> 01:37:29.227
Temporary crew members.

1359
01:37:29.228 --> 01:37:32.144
Welcome to the Navigation Platform ISS.

1360
01:37:32.145 --> 01:37:35.978
Please report to Docking Hall No. 4
at your earliest convenience.

1361
01:37:39.520 --> 01:37:40.520
Chief.

1362
01:37:56.229 --> 01:37:57.521
Have you been well?

1363
01:38:01.187 --> 01:38:02.187
Yes.

1364
01:38:23.522 --> 01:38:24.896
Mr. Zhou.

1365
01:38:24.897 --> 01:38:27.146
The image you requested is ready.

1366
01:38:27.147 --> 01:38:28.147
Okay.

1367
01:38:29.522 --> 01:38:30.772
It's almost time.

1368
01:38:33.397 --> 01:38:34.397
Okay.

1369
01:38:39.563 --> 01:38:47.563
[50 hours to the Moon disintegrates]

1370
01:39:21.023 --> 01:39:22.023
All right.

1371
01:39:24.439 --> 01:39:25.938
Mr. President.

1372
01:39:27.356 --> 01:39:28.980
Delegates.

1373
01:39:28.981 --> 01:39:31.438
Everyone around the world.

1374
01:39:31.439 --> 01:39:36.730
This is a piece of fossil
from 15.000 years ago.

1375
01:39:36.731 --> 01:39:40.356
It's a fractured human femur that healed.

1376
01:39:41.273 --> 01:39:44.440
It is the symbol of the
birth of human civilization.

1377
01:39:46.274 --> 01:39:49.024
15.000 years ago.

1378
01:39:49.732 --> 01:39:52.149
a thigh fracture is fatal.

1379
01:39:52.899 --> 01:39:55.940
Because you wouldn't be able
to avoid danger and forage.

1380
01:39:57.024 --> 01:40:00.564
You can only wait in place
to be eaten by wild beasts.

1381
01:40:00.565 --> 01:40:01.565
However.

1382
01:40:02.690 --> 01:40:06.190
this femur healed.

1383
01:40:06.982 --> 01:40:10.564
It means that after he got hurt.

1384
01:40:10.565 --> 01:40:13.689
someone dressed his wound.

1385
01:40:13.690 --> 01:40:17.398
Someone provided him with water and food.

1386
01:40:17.399 --> 01:40:22.190
Someone protected him
from the attacks of wild beasts.

1387
01:40:23.191 --> 01:40:26.940
This kind of interaction and solidarity

1388
01:40:26.941 --> 01:40:31.566
enabled us to survive and
continue civilization.

1389
01:40:33.691 --> 01:40:35.690
In 2044.

1390
01:40:35.691 --> 01:40:38.524
after the Lunar Exile
Project experiment succeeded.

1391
01:40:38.525 --> 01:40:42.024
we once proposed a backup plan.

1392
01:40:42.025 --> 01:40:46.940
Detonate our nuclear weapons on
the Moon's surface in a phased array.

1393
01:40:46.941 --> 01:40:50.815
triggering lunar nuclear fusion.
self-explosion. and disintegration.

1394
01:40:50.816 --> 01:40:57.566
The delegates here from
33 countries received...

1395
01:40:58.400 --> 01:41:00.650
the same message as I did.

1396
01:41:01.691 --> 01:41:06.442
This is the exact number of
deployable nuclear weapons worldwide.

1397
01:41:08.017 --> 01:41:13.109
It's also the total number of nuclear weapons
required to trigger lunar nuclear fusion.

1398
01:41:18.442 --> 01:41:22.816
These numbers were once top secret.

1399
01:41:22.817 --> 01:41:25.526
but they're pointless now.

1400
01:41:28.192 --> 01:41:33.775
I don't know the source and
intent of this information.

1401
01:41:33.776 --> 01:41:37.734
But it seems to be
reminding us of something.

1402
01:41:38.400 --> 01:41:42.108
15.000 years later.

1403
01:41:42.109 --> 01:41:46.652
if another fractured
femur is in front of us.

1404
01:41:47.693 --> 01:41:55.693
will we still make the same choice
as they did 15.000 years ago?

1405
01:42:08.985 --> 01:42:11.517
Your slot in the underground
city is canceled.

1406
01:42:12.527 --> 01:42:14.068
It's fine. Mr. Ma.

1407
01:42:15.977 --> 01:42:18.402
I proved that I was right.

1408
01:42:20.193 --> 01:42:21.277
Does it matter?

1409
01:42:24.653 --> 01:42:25.944
To Yaya.

1410
01:42:27.236 --> 01:42:28.611
it matters a lot.

1411
01:42:29.485 --> 01:42:33.694
Is Yaya. who got a complete life.
an angel or a demon?

1412
01:42:39.444 --> 01:42:41.862
Mr. Ma. don't worry.

1413
01:42:42.736 --> 01:42:43.902
As long as there's enough time...

1414
01:42:43.903 --> 01:42:45.198
There's no more time.

1415
01:42:46.111 --> 01:42:47.778
The Lunar Exile Project failed.

1416
01:42:47.779 --> 01:42:49.279
Earth must set off immediately.

1417
01:42:50.569 --> 01:42:54.069
To control the Earth Engines worldwide.
we need to restore the Internet.

1418
01:42:55.986 --> 01:42:58.986
After we stopped rotating. the sea water
flooded the root server in Beijing.

1419
01:42:59.944 --> 01:43:02.110
It's extremely difficult to reboot it.

1420
01:43:02.111 --> 01:43:03.528
Why me?

1421
01:43:05.279 --> 01:43:08.486
According to the logs. 1.7 seconds
after Yaya was successfully uploaded.

1422
01:43:08.487 --> 01:43:10.654
the lunar satellite engines
started to overload.

1423
01:43:11.779 --> 01:43:13.730
I don't think that was a coincidence.

1424
01:43:21.279 --> 01:43:22.612
Then can I...

1425
01:43:23.904 --> 01:43:24.904
decline?

1426
01:43:29.695 --> 01:43:30.987
I don't think you will.

1427
01:43:41.612 --> 01:43:45.612
Our mission this time
is to set up nuclear bombs on the Moon.

1428
01:43:45.613 --> 01:43:47.529
Step forward when you're called.

1429
01:43:47.530 --> 01:43:48.987
Peter Walsh.

1430
01:43:48.988 --> 01:43:50.070
Here!

1431
01:43:50.071 --> 01:43:51.737
Neil Drofa.

1432
01:43:51.738 --> 01:43:53.029
Here!

1433
01:43:53.030 --> 01:43:54.030
Don't worry.

1434
01:43:55.070 --> 01:43:57.569
- It has already been arranged.
- Liu Peiqiang.

1435
01:43:57.570 --> 01:43:58.570
Here!

1436
01:43:59.738 --> 01:44:00.988
- Chief.
- Nov.

1437
01:44:03.280 --> 01:44:05.703
You did it on purpose. didn't you?

1438
01:44:06.779 --> 01:44:09.320
They're chosen based on
their flight exam results.

1439
01:44:09.321 --> 01:44:11.945
You won't get to go even if you want to.

1440
01:44:11.946 --> 01:44:12.946
Just wait.

1441
01:44:14.196 --> 01:44:15.196
Chief.

1442
01:44:15.197 --> 01:44:16.352
I must go.

1443
01:44:17.112 --> 01:44:20.238
My son is down there.
I need to be stationed here.

1444
01:44:21.821 --> 01:44:24.946
The Lunar Crisis response
plan has three steps.

1445
01:44:24.947 --> 01:44:25.906
First step.

1446
01:44:25.907 --> 01:44:28.988
Transport the world's nuclear arsenal
to the Moon using the space station.

1447
01:44:28.989 --> 01:44:30.363
In a phased array.

1448
01:44:30.364 --> 01:44:33.822
set them up in the Campanus Crater.
which has a diameter of 46 km.

1449
01:44:36.363 --> 01:44:38.988
Lunar debris has formed an asteroid belt.

1450
01:44:38.989 --> 01:44:43.405
The Navigation Platform ISS
will maintain in high orbit.

1451
01:44:43.406 --> 01:44:48.197
All nuclear weapons are packaged.
counting 3.750 in total.

1452
01:44:52.822 --> 01:44:54.988
Enter the bomb set-up position.

1453
01:44:54.989 --> 01:44:57.655
All bomb setup personnel.
prepare for departure.

1454
01:44:57.656 --> 01:45:02.198
Be sure to complete the mission
before entering the Roche limit.

1455
01:45:03.197 --> 01:45:04.114
Second step.

1456
01:45:04.115 --> 01:45:05.906
Connect all the nuclear weapons.

1457
01:45:05.907 --> 01:45:08.740
Using the Space Station as a relay
satellite. detonate them remotely.

1458
01:45:11.073 --> 01:45:14.782
It will trigger lunar nuclear fusion. causing
the Moon to collapse and disintegrate.

1459
01:45:16.240 --> 01:45:18.947
[UEG Temporary Command Center]

1460
01:45:18.948 --> 01:45:20.906
Don't talk to me about redundancy.

1461
01:45:20.907 --> 01:45:21.823
Get away!

1462
01:45:21.824 --> 01:45:23.781
I can't magically pull 3.000
engines out of thin air.

1463
01:45:23.782 --> 01:45:26.656
Headquarters has received the encrypted
data of all nuclear weapons worldwide.

1464
01:45:26.657 --> 01:45:31.072
To remotely detonate them. these must be
split. decrypted. and serially connected.

1465
01:45:31.073 --> 01:45:32.864
Nuclear files have arrived.

1466
01:45:32.865 --> 01:45:36.345
Please make serial connection as soon as
possible. [UEG Temporary Weapon Control Center]

1467
01:45:36.573 --> 01:45:37.573
Thank you.

1468
01:45:38.490 --> 01:45:40.531
550W has been connected to the decryptor.

1469
01:45:40.532 --> 01:45:45.198
These data have been created
between 1945 and 2045.

1470
01:45:45.199 --> 01:45:49.157
Different countries used
different encryption systems.

1471
01:45:49.158 --> 01:45:53.157
Regular decoding would
take at least ten years.

1472
01:45:53.158 --> 01:45:59.448
But we only have half a day
to string them together.

1473
01:45:59.449 --> 01:46:00.490
Third step.

1474
01:46:00.491 --> 01:46:04.490
Reboot the root servers in
Dulles. Tokyo. and Beijing.

1475
01:46:04.491 --> 01:46:08.157
Restore the Internet
to initiate the Earth Engines worldwide.

1476
01:46:08.158 --> 01:46:10.823
evade the lunar debris.
and embark on a new journey.

1477
01:46:10.824 --> 01:46:14.115
All of the 7.000 Earth Engines
have opened their network ports

1478
01:46:14.116 --> 01:46:15.990
and ready for Internet connection.

1479
01:46:15.991 --> 01:46:19.574
Inform Advance Teams
in Dulles. Beijing. and Tokyo to set off.

1480
01:46:20.866 --> 01:46:25.198
The task of bringing the root name servers
back online has begun.

1481
01:46:25.199 --> 01:46:27.784
After the nuclear bombs go off. we only have
30 minutes to ignite the Earth Engines.

1482
01:46:27.785 --> 01:46:29.840
Otherwise. we can't
escape the lunar debris.

1483
01:46:33.284 --> 01:46:35.158
The engines' private
network isn't completed yet.

1484
01:46:35.159 --> 01:46:37.784
The only way to ignite it
is to restore the Internet.

1485
01:46:39.824 --> 01:46:41.574
This is the key to restoring the Internet.

1486
01:46:41.575 --> 01:46:44.408
The password is 30.000 random numbers
generated in real-time.

1487
01:46:44.409 --> 01:46:47.783
Only this can access the Internet
and connect all engines.

1488
01:46:47.784 --> 01:46:49.158
Once the engines are connected.

1489
01:46:49.159 --> 01:46:52.849
550W will rewrite their operating systems
to standardize the ignition command.

1490
01:46:56.574 --> 01:46:58.408
I brought you what you asked for.

1491
01:46:58.409 --> 01:46:59.409
Thank you.

1492
01:47:01.867 --> 01:47:02.867
Benben.

1493
01:47:04.074 --> 01:47:05.408
This is a waterproof spray.

1494
01:47:05.409 --> 01:47:09.575
It forms a thin film on the object's surface
to achieve a strong hydrophobic effect and...

1495
01:47:09.576 --> 01:47:11.435
You can write anything
else you want to say.

1496
01:47:16.243 --> 01:47:17.575
Thank you.

1497
01:47:17.576 --> 01:47:19.138
I don't know who to write to.

1498
01:47:26.581 --> 01:47:27.992
Hurry. sync up.

1499
01:47:27.993 --> 01:47:29.401
Check the equipment.

1500
01:47:30.285 --> 01:47:32.534
Underwater docking cable installed.

1501
01:47:32.535 --> 01:47:33.785
Contact the commander!

1502
01:47:33.786 --> 01:47:35.128
Prepare to go into the water!

1503
01:48:02.661 --> 01:48:03.785
Mr. Zhou.

1504
01:48:03.786 --> 01:48:05.331
They've connected the
nuclear weapons worldwide.

1505
01:48:05.332 --> 01:48:08.118
We have 12 hours before the Moon falls.

1506
01:48:08.119 --> 01:48:09.619
The rain stopped.

1507
01:48:11.369 --> 01:48:13.077
Let's begin.

1508
01:48:16.356 --> 01:48:21.035
[12 hours to the Moon disintegrates]

1509
01:48:38.162 --> 01:48:40.536
The number you have
dialed cannot be reached.

1510
01:48:40.537 --> 01:48:44.744
Most satellites were destroyed
by the Moon's debris.

1511
01:48:44.745 --> 01:48:46.543
I called my daughter.

1512
01:48:46.544 --> 01:48:48.452
I couldn't reach her.

1513
01:48:48.453 --> 01:48:50.661
I'm here. don't worry.

1514
01:48:50.662 --> 01:48:53.411
I'll take good care of you.

1515
01:48:53.412 --> 01:48:55.494
The diving suit is made of aluminum alloy.

1516
01:48:55.495 --> 01:48:57.827
It's 240 kg in weight and 2.1 m in height.

1517
01:48:57.828 --> 01:49:01.494
With the foot control thruster. control your
direction through the foot pedal device.

1518
01:49:01.495 --> 01:49:02.869
Mind your depth.

1519
01:49:02.870 --> 01:49:05.286
Check residual air every five minutes.

1520
01:49:05.287 --> 01:49:06.619
Pay attention to the
pressure gauge warning.

1521
01:49:06.620 --> 01:49:09.496
That is the lighter transporter.

1522
01:49:12.412 --> 01:49:14.954
You're going down there soon.
Are you scared?

1523
01:49:25.037 --> 01:49:29.287
The Advance Team to restore the Internet
have arrived at the designated locations.

1524
01:49:29.288 --> 01:49:30.745
Yes. okay.

1525
01:49:30.746 --> 01:49:32.328
Yes. I understand.

1526
01:49:32.329 --> 01:49:35.453
The Internet Restoration Operation is a go.

1527
01:49:35.454 --> 01:49:39.371
Dulles. Tokyo. and Beijing
Advance Team on standby.

1528
01:49:40.871 --> 01:49:43.079
Begin nuclear weapons decryption.

1529
01:49:43.080 --> 01:49:45.039
Unencrypted count. 3.143.

1530
01:49:47.264 --> 01:49:49.930
We have 12 hours until the Moon
reaches the Roche limit.

1531
01:49:49.931 --> 01:49:51.389
The countdown starts now.

1532
01:49:53.872 --> 01:49:56.538
Inform all airships to prepare for launch.

1533
01:49:56.539 --> 01:49:59.247
Communication equipment testing completed.

1534
01:50:10.497 --> 01:50:11.633
Five seconds.

1535
01:50:11.634 --> 01:50:13.634
Shuttle 33. stand by.

1536
01:50:15.164 --> 01:50:16.496
Final checks.

1537
01:50:16.497 --> 01:50:18.122
Prepare to go into the water.

1538
01:50:18.123 --> 01:50:19.123
Launch.

1539
01:50:38.956 --> 01:50:40.254
Benben!

1540
01:50:40.255 --> 01:50:41.672
You're a military dog!

1541
01:51:02.165 --> 01:51:06.208
[4 hours to Internet recovery]

1542
01:51:30.249 --> 01:51:35.374
[Big Sale]

1543
01:51:36.124 --> 01:51:37.621
Things finally got cheaper.

1544
01:51:42.624 --> 01:51:43.624
Mr. Ma.

1545
01:51:44.416 --> 01:51:45.707
What are these?

1546
01:51:46.541 --> 01:51:47.541
Hair tails.

1547
01:51:48.375 --> 01:51:50.356
When they sleep. they stay vertical.

1548
01:52:08.958 --> 01:52:13.124
[China Internet Center. Beijing
Headquarters] [Former Site]

1549
01:52:13.125 --> 01:52:15.791
Transport vessel No. 34 setting off.

1550
01:52:15.792 --> 01:52:18.166
It will reach position in 35 minutes.

1551
01:52:18.167 --> 01:52:21.082
Direction adjustment done.
Vision is normal. speeding up.

1552
01:52:21.083 --> 01:52:23.582
No. 16. maintain the formation.

1553
01:52:23.583 --> 01:52:25.666
You are on my emergency avoidance route.

1554
01:52:25.667 --> 01:52:26.916
Do you copy?

1555
01:52:26.917 --> 01:52:29.375
I repeat. Do you copy?

1556
01:52:29.376 --> 01:52:34.833
Clusters of lunar debris spotted on Radar.
not yet within visual range.

1557
01:52:34.834 --> 01:52:37.292
Collision avoidance
system warning received.

1558
01:52:37.293 --> 01:52:39.167
Route to be changed.

1559
01:52:39.168 --> 01:52:40.792
Lunar debris spotted.

1560
01:52:40.793 --> 01:52:43.251
Small-scale auxiliary
radar has been activated.

1561
01:52:44.293 --> 01:52:45.364
No. 11 exploded!

1562
01:52:45.365 --> 01:52:47.074
Avoid the debris from the shock wave!

1563
01:52:51.459 --> 01:52:52.376
I'm doomed.

1564
01:52:52.377 --> 01:52:54.958
- Mom. come and protect me.
- Don't get distracted. Focus.

1565
01:52:54.959 --> 01:52:56.500
No. 26. speed up.

1566
01:52:56.501 --> 01:52:59.125
God. let me have another nshima. okay?

1567
01:52:59.126 --> 01:53:01.875
No.33. if you can hear me. please respond.

1568
01:53:01.876 --> 01:53:03.334
200 warheads were lost.
[Lost contact]

1569
01:53:03.335 --> 01:53:05.224
We have 180 left in the redundant array.

1570
01:53:12.085 --> 01:53:13.126
Emilia.

1571
01:53:13.127 --> 01:53:14.127
Advance.

1572
01:53:19.669 --> 01:53:21.168
Designated coordinates reached.

1573
01:53:21.169 --> 01:53:22.335
Initiate bomb setup mode.

1574
01:53:25.794 --> 01:53:27.584
Engage autopilot.

1575
01:53:27.585 --> 01:53:30.502
Set the uniform flight
speed to 180 km per hour.

1576
01:53:32.169 --> 01:53:35.710
550W will assist in setting up the
nuclear bombs in their accurate positions.

1577
01:53:37.544 --> 01:53:39.425
The energy required to
completely destroy the Moon

1578
01:53:39.426 --> 01:53:42.251
is 1B times the total
yield of nuclear weapons.

1579
01:53:42.252 --> 01:53:45.752
The bombs we've gathered
can barely count as a lead wire.

1580
01:53:46.710 --> 01:53:48.919
So the placements must be accurate...

1581
01:53:50.253 --> 01:53:52.982
to ensure the phased array
element focus point is accurate.

1582
01:54:25.961 --> 01:54:30.319
[3 hours to nuclear explosion]

1583
01:54:42.962 --> 01:54:44.928
Hurry. I think it won't hold for long.

1584
01:54:46.296 --> 01:54:47.928
Let's go down the elevator entrance.

1585
01:54:50.879 --> 01:54:52.670
It's on the 17th floor below.

1586
01:54:52.671 --> 01:54:54.421
Good thing it's not the 18th.

1587
01:54:55.962 --> 01:54:58.878
Upon scanning. there's a cavity
area on the 17th floor below.

1588
01:54:58.879 --> 01:55:01.253
Remember to turn off the propulsion system
to save power.

1589
01:55:01.254 --> 01:55:02.952
Third remaining oxygen level check.

1590
01:55:07.711 --> 01:55:09.378
That's the power distribution room.

1591
01:55:09.379 --> 01:55:11.546
Cai. go with Benben to restore power.

1592
01:55:11.547 --> 01:55:13.588
Xu. come with us to the
central control area.

1593
01:55:15.007 --> 01:55:17.207
[China Internet Center Beijing
Headquarters] Here it is.

1594
01:55:19.547 --> 01:55:21.671
Benben. go and help.

1595
01:55:21.672 --> 01:55:23.255
Benben. pull the cable in.

1596
01:55:36.130 --> 01:55:37.445
The power is back.

1597
01:55:44.012 --> 01:55:46.595
This is the world's biggest
liquid-cooled server cluster.

1598
01:55:47.680 --> 01:55:49.263
This is the real new world.

1599
01:55:50.214 --> 01:55:51.589
The card still doesn't work.

1600
01:55:58.506 --> 01:55:59.588
Lock it. hurry.

1601
01:55:59.589 --> 01:56:01.829
This is a high-pressure door.
It won't hold for too long.

1602
01:56:06.464 --> 01:56:08.172
Force feedback overload.

1603
01:56:08.173 --> 01:56:09.839
I can't hold on any longer.

1604
01:56:11.881 --> 01:56:13.071
My leg!

1605
01:56:23.006 --> 01:56:26.381
Almost there. Five nuclear bombs left.

1606
01:56:29.131 --> 01:56:32.133
Liu. we can finally go home.

1607
01:56:36.007 --> 01:56:37.382
Mayday!

1608
01:56:38.048 --> 01:56:39.506
Mayday!

1609
01:56:39.507 --> 01:56:40.715
Mayday!

1610
01:57:04.757 --> 01:57:07.464
We've lost contact with
Transport Vessel 10.

1611
01:57:07.465 --> 01:57:10.506
Sir. we lost contact with
Transport Vessel 33 too.

1612
01:57:10.507 --> 01:57:12.715
Confirm if there are survivors.

1613
01:57:12.716 --> 01:57:15.257
I need to confirm if there are survivors.

1614
01:57:15.258 --> 01:57:17.008
Continue calling it.

1615
01:57:18.883 --> 01:57:21.758
We've lost 384 warheads in total.
Redundancy at negative four.

1616
01:57:21.759 --> 01:57:23.676
The phased array fell
below the critical value.

1617
01:57:24.883 --> 01:57:27.926
550W is about to halt.
The system's gonna crash.

1618
01:57:29.883 --> 01:57:32.840
We've cracked 697 of them.

1619
01:57:32.841 --> 01:57:35.383
The Moon's nuclear bomb setup progress
is 95% complete.

1620
01:57:38.216 --> 01:57:40.508
Stop dawdling. Speed up!
[Lunar detonation countdown]

1621
01:57:41.300 --> 01:57:43.633
Three hours before
reaching the Roche limit.

1622
01:57:58.467 --> 01:57:59.907
Find a first-aid kit.

1623
01:58:01.008 --> 01:58:03.716
He's seriously wounded.
We must send him up at once.

1624
01:58:03.717 --> 01:58:05.550
Cai. come to the Central Control Room.

1625
01:58:05.551 --> 01:58:07.551
- Prepare to pull out.
- I'll be right there.

1626
01:58:21.926 --> 01:58:22.926
Hello?

1627
01:58:23.758 --> 01:58:25.216
- Can anyone hear me?
- Liu Peiqiang.

1628
01:58:25.217 --> 01:58:27.383
You're very low on oxygen.

1629
01:58:27.384 --> 01:58:29.008
Hang in there.

1630
01:58:29.009 --> 01:58:31.426
Our mission isn't complete yet.

1631
01:58:31.427 --> 01:58:36.259
The system indicates that five vessels
have crashed. including ours.

1632
01:58:36.260 --> 01:58:39.801
- Two survived.
- Mom. I want to go home.

1633
01:58:39.802 --> 01:58:42.842
The number of nuclear bombs we have
is below the detonation threshold.

1634
01:58:42.843 --> 01:58:46.426
The other survivors went to
set up the nuclear bombs.

1635
01:58:46.427 --> 01:58:49.510
We must find a way to
set up these five too.

1636
01:58:56.843 --> 01:58:59.510
The emergency return capsule is ahead.

1637
01:59:00.967 --> 01:59:02.467
Liu Peiqiang.

1638
01:59:02.468 --> 01:59:05.593
Check if any lunar rovers in the base
can be used.

1639
01:59:05.594 --> 01:59:07.072
Two bars of power left.

1640
01:59:07.843 --> 01:59:08.843
Great.

1641
01:59:13.928 --> 01:59:17.595
Leave first. I've already
set the automatic return.

1642
01:59:23.919 --> 01:59:26.885
We still have five nuclear bombs
to set up in our mission.

1643
01:59:26.886 --> 01:59:29.136
Don't worry. We trained
for so long in Libreville.

1644
01:59:29.137 --> 01:59:31.095
We have good teamwork.

1645
01:59:36.219 --> 01:59:39.343
Liu Peiqiang. we're not regularized yet.

1646
01:59:39.344 --> 01:59:40.927
We don't have medical insurance.

1647
01:59:40.928 --> 01:59:42.261
I know.

1648
01:59:42.262 --> 01:59:43.602
I won't be needing it.

1649
01:59:48.136 --> 01:59:49.054
Liu Peiqiang!

1650
01:59:49.055 --> 01:59:51.137
Why did you close the door again?

1651
01:59:52.512 --> 01:59:54.928
Liu Peiqiang! What are you doing?

1652
01:59:54.929 --> 01:59:57.705
You don't need two people
for five nuclear bombs.

1653
01:59:58.931 --> 02:00:00.136
There are only three seats.

1654
02:00:00.137 --> 02:00:01.886
It's not enough for me.

1655
02:00:01.887 --> 02:00:02.887
Go home.

1656
02:00:03.719 --> 02:00:05.594
Your daughter is waiting for you.

1657
02:00:05.595 --> 02:00:09.011
Liu Peiqiang. you still don't get it.

1658
02:00:09.012 --> 02:00:13.386
Without any tools.
how can you carry the five nuclear bombs?

1659
02:00:13.387 --> 02:00:14.554
Liu Peiqiang!

1660
02:00:15.554 --> 02:00:17.137
Come back!

1661
02:00:19.220 --> 02:00:21.637
Two hours and ten minutes left.

1662
02:00:22.345 --> 02:00:24.054
Why claw at it? Get a knife. idiot!

1663
02:00:26.228 --> 02:00:31.054
Sir. the group from the Space Station wants to
know how much longer before we break the codes.

1664
02:00:36.596 --> 02:00:37.929
Fuck off!

1665
02:00:37.930 --> 02:00:39.887
You think I don't want to know?

1666
02:00:39.888 --> 02:00:42.096
Go dig a grave and get me an encryptor!

1667
02:00:46.638 --> 02:00:49.420
Watch your keyboard. son.
The keyboard is your weapon.

1668
02:00:49.421 --> 02:00:52.175
[Lunar detonation countdown]

1669
02:01:01.430 --> 02:01:03.095
Stop looking.

1670
02:01:03.096 --> 02:01:04.678
Only one diving suit is left.

1671
02:01:05.638 --> 02:01:08.137
If we can't finish the work here.
[154 minutes to Internet recovery]

1672
02:01:08.138 --> 02:01:09.221
we'll all die.

1673
02:01:10.138 --> 02:01:11.179
Headquarters.

1674
02:01:11.180 --> 02:01:13.320
The wounded has arrived
at the root server's gate.

1675
02:01:13.321 --> 02:01:14.446
Please receive them.

1676
02:01:24.847 --> 02:01:27.222
Beijing Advance Team
suffered losses due to casualty.

1677
02:01:28.139 --> 02:01:31.055
Give me a sit-rep on Dulles Advance Team.

1678
02:01:31.056 --> 02:01:34.055
Give me a sit-rep on
Tokyo First Backup Team.

1679
02:01:34.056 --> 02:01:35.576
[Initiating automatic return program]

1680
02:01:45.472 --> 02:01:47.596
Sir. I received a return
signal from the Moon.

1681
02:01:47.597 --> 02:01:50.097
Provide the Space Station
return coordinates.

1682
02:01:57.640 --> 02:02:02.222
Access the Navigator Space
Station return coordinates.

1683
02:02:02.223 --> 02:02:05.015
Our relay base station
is on the transport boat.

1684
02:02:06.557 --> 02:02:09.140
He's out of communication range.

1685
02:02:13.140 --> 02:02:17.890
He'll probably die a
quiet death on the Moon.

1686
02:02:28.932 --> 02:02:29.973
Hurry.

1687
02:02:36.057 --> 02:02:37.807
I'll reboot the root server.

1688
02:02:37.808 --> 02:02:40.348
Physically connect 500W
and the root server.

1689
02:02:40.349 --> 02:02:43.848
Once they're connected. let 550W into
the Earth Engine control the network.

1690
02:02:43.849 --> 02:02:46.168
It will perform real-time analysis
of the Earth Engines worldwide

1691
02:02:46.169 --> 02:02:47.849
and generate a temporary operating system.

1692
02:03:08.349 --> 02:03:09.349
The door is broken.

1693
02:03:11.016 --> 02:03:12.433
Why must it be broken now?

1694
02:03:14.184 --> 02:03:16.024
Backup Team 1 reached
the designated position.

1695
02:03:16.850 --> 02:03:17.767
Push!

1696
02:03:17.768 --> 02:03:19.392
Backup Team 2 will arrive in 15 minutes.

1697
02:03:19.393 --> 02:03:21.033
Backup Team 3 will set off in 15 minutes.

1698
02:03:26.725 --> 02:03:28.974
Mr. Ma. the progress is stuck.

1699
02:03:28.975 --> 02:03:30.599
It can't be recovered.

1700
02:03:30.600 --> 02:03:32.972
Without hardware support.
you can't recover anything.

1701
02:03:35.517 --> 02:03:37.010
There's still one unconnected.

1702
02:03:43.225 --> 02:03:44.850
It's too fucking cold.

1703
02:04:28.559 --> 02:04:32.350
After two hours. the Moon
will breach the Roche limit.

1704
02:04:32.351 --> 02:04:34.393
We must detonate the nuclear bombs ASAP.

1705
02:04:34.394 --> 02:04:37.768
After detonation. we must ignite
the engines within 30 minutes.

1706
02:04:37.769 --> 02:04:41.935
Once the lunar debris breaches the
Roche limit. we won't be able to escape.

1707
02:04:41.936 --> 02:04:44.560
Everything on the surface of the Earth
will be destroyed.

1708
02:04:44.561 --> 02:04:45.811
Yes. I understand.

1709
02:04:45.812 --> 02:04:48.020
But we need another 13 warheads...

1710
02:04:50.729 --> 02:04:52.932
[Warning]

1711
02:05:09.727 --> 02:05:13.065
Hurry up! Get to the
underground bunkers now!

1712
02:05:14.602 --> 02:05:16.727
Ms. Hao. should we...

1713
02:05:16.728 --> 02:05:19.901
At a time like this. nowhere is safe.

1714
02:05:29.853 --> 02:05:32.852
We've lost contact with Backup Team 1!

1715
02:05:32.853 --> 02:05:34.352
Second Backup Team is here.

1716
02:05:34.353 --> 02:05:36.477
Third Backup Team. 13 mikes.

1717
02:05:36.478 --> 02:05:39.061
Second. Tokyo. Third.
Dulles Team oscar mike.

1718
02:05:39.062 --> 02:05:40.436
Fourth Team. stand by.

1719
02:05:40.437 --> 02:05:41.686
Mr. Ma.

1720
02:05:41.687 --> 02:05:43.227
The hardware connection is done.

1721
02:05:43.228 --> 02:05:45.353
I'll be out at once. Last set of passwords.

1722
02:06:00.646 --> 02:06:01.978
Tu Hengyu!

1723
02:06:01.979 --> 02:06:03.146
Come here!

1724
02:06:04.729 --> 02:06:06.563
Hurry! My leg is stuck.

1725
02:06:19.813 --> 02:06:21.021
Tu Hengyu. hurry!

1726
02:06:21.022 --> 02:06:22.713
Benben. come and help me!

1727
02:06:28.729 --> 02:06:30.438
Tu Hengyu. hurry.

1728
02:06:41.022 --> 02:06:42.022
Tu Hengyu.

1729
02:06:43.064 --> 02:06:44.064
Catch!

1730
02:06:44.897 --> 02:06:46.564
Last set of passwords.

1731
02:06:48.771 --> 02:06:50.271
Remember.

1732
02:06:50.272 --> 02:06:54.314
A civilization without
humans is meaningless.

1733
02:07:49.023 --> 02:07:51.065
The Moon is getting closer.

1734
02:07:56.349 --> 02:07:59.661
[London 01 Earth Engine]

1735
02:08:09.316 --> 02:08:13.590
[Sydney - Former Site]

1736
02:08:13.591 --> 02:08:17.869
[Toronto No.2 Underground City Gate 09]

1737
02:08:35.446 --> 02:08:39.290
[Beijing No.3 Underground City Gate 52]

1738
02:08:44.358 --> 02:08:45.399
No pushing!

1739
02:08:45.400 --> 02:08:47.275
Stop pushing!

1740
02:08:49.232 --> 02:08:50.441
There's no time.

1741
02:08:50.442 --> 02:08:52.122
- There's no way we can finish this.
- Sir.

1742
02:08:52.733 --> 02:08:55.608
You know it's too hard.

1743
02:08:56.316 --> 02:08:59.399
All nuclear bombs came
from different models.

1744
02:08:59.400 --> 02:09:04.024
eras. and countries.

1745
02:09:04.025 --> 02:09:05.732
Get to the point.

1746
02:09:05.733 --> 02:09:08.316
How much longer do you need?

1747
02:09:08.317 --> 02:09:11.483
The Moon's nuclear bombs are all set up.

1748
02:09:19.443 --> 02:09:23.818
We need at least 714 hours.

1749
02:09:41.568 --> 02:09:43.109
Mankind...

1750
02:09:45.443 --> 02:09:49.193
used the most sophisticated
security system...

1751
02:09:50.901 --> 02:09:54.568
to destroy each other.

1752
02:10:00.152 --> 02:10:01.152
Sir.

1753
02:10:05.444 --> 02:10:08.485
We have another backup plan.
[53 minutes to nuclear explosion]

1754
02:10:11.319 --> 02:10:14.901
This is a mechanical
detonator for a nuclear bomb.

1755
02:10:14.902 --> 02:10:16.193
This is the trigger.

1756
02:10:16.194 --> 02:10:19.776
There are 81 models in total.

1757
02:10:19.777 --> 02:10:23.109
- For each nuclear bomb we detonate.
- This is the safety.

1758
02:10:23.110 --> 02:10:24.859
- Ten more around it...
- This is the trigger.

1759
02:10:24.860 --> 02:10:26.859
Can be triggered.

1760
02:10:26.860 --> 02:10:29.734
- The hydrogen bombs need to be detonated one by one.
- This is the safety.

1761
02:10:29.735 --> 02:10:31.318
- So...
- and the trigger.

1762
02:10:31.319 --> 02:10:33.943
We need...

1763
02:10:33.944 --> 02:10:38.360
- 219 people for this operation.
- Safety. Trigger.

1764
02:10:38.361 --> 02:10:44.569
To guarantee our success.
we need 300 people.

1765
02:10:44.570 --> 02:10:47.872
Our docking modules aren't landing crafts.

1766
02:10:47.873 --> 02:10:49.110
This is the trigger.

1767
02:10:49.111 --> 02:10:52.153
So I only have a one-way ticket.

1768
02:10:53.320 --> 02:10:55.902
Russian ones are without safety.

1769
02:10:55.903 --> 02:10:58.485
We've got two triggers.

1770
02:10:58.486 --> 02:10:59.486
I'll go!

1771
02:11:00.611 --> 02:11:02.610
I'm in!

1772
02:11:02.611 --> 02:11:03.652
I'll go!

1773
02:11:03.653 --> 02:11:04.819
I'm in!

1774
02:11:04.820 --> 02:11:07.277
- I'll go!
- I'm in!

1775
02:11:07.278 --> 02:11:08.860
- I'll go!
- I'm in!

1776
02:11:08.861 --> 02:11:11.902
- I'll go!
- I'll go!

1777
02:11:11.903 --> 02:11:13.569
- Let me go!
- I'll go.

1778
02:11:13.570 --> 02:11:14.986
- I'll go.
- Let me join!

1779
02:11:16.486 --> 02:11:18.196
- I'm in!
- I'll go!

1780
02:11:23.737 --> 02:11:25.160
What are you looking at?

1781
02:11:26.821 --> 02:11:28.279
The Moon is ours.

1782
02:11:29.237 --> 02:11:31.892
I don't feel at ease to let
you youngsters handle it.

1783
02:11:36.487 --> 02:11:38.862
Chinese Aerospace Squadron!

1784
02:11:41.487 --> 02:11:43.196
Everyone over 50.

1785
02:11:45.112 --> 02:11:46.778
step forward!

1786
02:11:46.779 --> 02:11:48.028
Makarov.

1787
02:11:48.029 --> 02:11:49.445
Remember.

1788
02:11:49.446 --> 02:11:52.778
We Russians are invincible in space.

1789
02:11:52.779 --> 02:11:56.611
Russian Aerospace Squadron!
Everyone over 50. step forward!

1790
02:11:56.612 --> 02:11:57.695
US squadron!

1791
02:11:57.696 --> 02:12:00.904
- France Aerospace Squadron!
- Everyone over 50. step forward!

1792
02:12:00.905 --> 02:12:02.321
- Thailand Aerospace Squadron!
- Brazil Aerospace Squadron!

1793
02:12:02.322 --> 02:12:04.612
- Everyone over 50. step forward!
- Everyone over 50. step forward!

1794
02:12:04.613 --> 02:12:08.029
Singapore Aerospace Squadron!
Everyone over 50. step forward!

1795
02:12:08.030 --> 02:12:10.190
South Korean Aerospace Squadron!
Everyone over 50. step forward!

1796
02:12:10.191 --> 02:12:13.613
British squadron!
People over 50. please step forward!

1797
02:12:15.613 --> 02:12:16.655
Attention!

1798
02:12:18.197 --> 02:12:19.322
Salute!

1799
02:12:26.205 --> 02:12:29.205
I hope the world remembers this day.

1800
02:12:38.489 --> 02:12:39.823
Xiaoxi.

1801
02:12:40.906 --> 02:12:43.198
Do you think this is fair?

1802
02:12:50.823 --> 02:12:52.781
In the face of crisis.

1803
02:12:53.781 --> 02:12:56.114
only responsibility exists.

1804
02:13:51.907 --> 02:13:53.824
Backup Team 2 is in position.

1805
02:14:06.700 --> 02:14:08.032
Benben.

1806
02:14:08.033 --> 02:14:09.282
Go ahead.

1807
02:14:09.283 --> 02:14:12.158
I don't think I can get out.

1808
02:14:13.200 --> 02:14:15.575
Don't be afraid. I'm here.

1809
02:14:38.608 --> 02:14:42.760
[14 minutes to nuclear explosion]

1810
02:14:42.761 --> 02:14:44.812
[Oxygen remaining time]

1811
02:15:59.202 --> 02:16:00.743
I can't hear you.

1812
02:16:00.744 --> 02:16:03.368
Zhang Peng. I saw your apprentice.

1813
02:16:03.369 --> 02:16:04.410
That's great!

1814
02:16:04.411 --> 02:16:06.702
His base station is damaged.

1815
02:16:06.703 --> 02:16:08.994
He can't hear us.

1816
02:16:12.244 --> 02:16:13.493
Where are you?

1817
02:16:13.494 --> 02:16:15.202
I'll go and find you.

1818
02:16:15.203 --> 02:16:17.202
Save the trouble.

1819
02:16:17.203 --> 02:16:21.620
Buddy. we're 20 km apart.

1820
02:16:25.119 --> 02:16:26.391
Stop bugging me.

1821
02:16:30.453 --> 02:16:31.536
Get lost.

1822
02:16:32.869 --> 02:16:34.243
Nov.

1823
02:16:34.244 --> 02:16:35.452
Yes?

1824
