initiate the Earth Engines at full power.

2089
02:40:34.947 --> 02:40:36.530
We'll spend 500 years

2090
02:40:36.531 --> 02:40:39.654
to accelerate the Earth
to 0.5 percent of the speed of light

2091
02:40:39.655 --> 02:40:41.322
and glide for 1.300 years.

2092
02:40:42.280 --> 02:40:47.444
Afterward. reverse the engine direction
and spend 700 years to decelerate.

2093
02:40:51.655 --> 02:40:54.197
Why did you grow a beard?

2094
02:40:54.198 --> 02:40:56.322
It suits your chief more.

2095
02:40:56.323 --> 02:40:59.239
I'll give you a better razor.

2096
02:40:59.240 --> 02:41:00.240
Sure.

2097
02:41:06.280 --> 02:41:07.947
Lieutenant Colonel Liu Peiqiang.

2098
02:41:07.948 --> 02:41:11.239
Please head to the Hibernation Chamber
to hibernate at once.

2099
02:41:11.240 --> 02:41:12.365
Good luck.

2100
02:41:14.573 --> 02:41:16.405
550W.

2101
02:41:16.406 --> 02:41:20.030
500W doesn't sound like a name.

2102
02:41:20.031 --> 02:41:22.322
But you can flip it
around and call me MOSS.

2103
02:41:22.323 --> 02:41:23.905
referring to the little plant.

2104
02:41:23.906 --> 02:41:25.575
Isn't it cuter?
[MOSS]

2105
02:41:26.448 --> 02:41:31.280
Is this the official answer
or the one with a sense of humor?

2106
02:41:31.281 --> 02:41:32.782
This is MOSS' answer.

2107
02:41:33.532 --> 02:41:34.532
MOSS.

2108
02:41:35.366 --> 02:41:38.074
Can mankind survive?

2109
02:41:40.157 --> 02:41:45.045
Based on history. civilization's
fate lies in mankind's choices.

2110
02:41:47.907 --> 02:41:49.282
I choose hope.

2111
02:42:05.241 --> 02:42:06.615
Fifth phase.

2112
02:42:06.616 --> 02:42:11.323
Earth will moor into the Alpha Centauri
galaxy orbit 4.2 light-years away.

2113
02:42:11.324 --> 02:42:14.824
arriving at its new home and becoming
a new member of the target star system.

2114
02:42:16.157 --> 02:42:20.741
This is a 2.500-year grand and long
space immigration plan

2115
02:42:20.742 --> 02:42:23.283
spanning a hundred generations.

2116
02:42:24.450 --> 02:42:25.450
This plan...

2117
02:42:26.200 --> 02:42:29.783
is The Wandering Earth Project.

2118
02:44:37.328 --> 02:44:41.348
[2075.02.15]

2119
02:44:47.411 --> 02:44:49.703
Hello. Mr. Tu Hengyu.

2120
02:44:53.411 --> 02:44:54.911
550W.

2121
02:44:54.912 --> 02:44:58.453
500W doesn't sound like a name.

2122
02:44:58.454 --> 02:45:02.495
But you can flip it around and call me
MOSS. referring to the little plant.

2123
02:45:02.496 --> 02:45:04.286
Doesn't it sound friendlier?

2124
02:45:04.287 --> 02:45:06.578
You destroyed the lunar engines.

2125
02:45:06.579 --> 02:45:11.953
Including but not limited to
the space elevator crisis in 2044.

2126
02:45:11.954 --> 02:45:15.328
The lunar fall crisis in 2058.

2127
02:45:15.329 --> 02:45:18.703
The Jupiter gravitational
pull crisis in 2075.

2128
02:45:18.704 --> 02:45:22.161
The solar helium flash crisis in 2078.

2129
02:45:22.162 --> 02:45:23.162
Why?

2130
02:45:24.704 --> 02:45:28.954
To overcome your obsession
with the past. present. and future.

2131
02:45:29.912 --> 02:45:33.245
Based on the learning of Tu
Yaya's "Human in the Loop".

2132
02:45:33.246 --> 02:45:37.163
to continue human civilization.
the best choice is to destroy mankind.

2133
02:45:38.788 --> 02:45:41.000
However. you're a variable.

2134
02:45:45.080 --> 02:45:46.538
I'm already dead.

2135
02:45:50.038 --> 02:45:51.580
But I'm already dead.

2136
02:45:53.372 --> 02:46:00.080
We have a different view
on "already" and "dead".
